%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20family's%20%246%2C300%20vacation%20was%20at%20risk%20when%20the%20passport%20office%20lost%20their%20daughter's%20photo%20and%20replaced%20it%20with%20the%20wrong%20child%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jasmeen%20Basi%20and%20her%20family.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fd8cca895d822030333e2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223020%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJasmeen%20Basi%20and%20her%20family.%3Cp%3EJasmeen%20Basi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJasmeen%20Basi%20and%20Dillon%20Birring%20spent%20more%20than%C2%A0%246%2C300%20on%20a%20trip%20to%20Egypt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20their%20first%20time%20together%20abroad%2C%20and%20their%20daughters%20needed%20passports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBasi%20said%20the%20UK%20passport%20office%20lost%20her%203-year-old's%20photo%20and%20used%20an%20older%20child's%20photo%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJasmeen%20Basi%20and%20Dillon%20Birring's%20family%20vacation%20was%20quickly%20approaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20their%20first%20trip%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fromantic-destinations-places-family-travel-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabroad%20as%20a%20family%20of%20four%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20March%2C%20they'd%20travel%20from%20their%20home%20in%20England%20to%20Egypt%20on%20an%20eight-day%20trip%20that%20cost%20them%20about%20%246%2C300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasi%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20did%20everything%20right.%20They%20booked%20the%20trip%20three%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20and%20shortly%20after%2C%20she%20began%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-a-passport%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassport%20application%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20herself%20and%20her%20two%20daughters%2C%20Sofia%2C%205%2C%20and%20Daya%2C%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasi's%20passport%20arrived%20in%20about%20two%20weeks%2C%20and%20Sofia's%20took%20even%20less%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20weeks%20went%20by%2C%20and%20the%20family%20still%20hadn't%20received%20Daya's.%20Finally%2C%20Basi%20said%20she%20got%20an%20update%20from%20a%20worker%20that%20there%20had%20been%20a%20mistake%3A%20Daya's%20photo%20had%20been%20misplaced%20with%20another%20child's%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20UK's%20passport%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-hampshire-68606355%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20representative%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpassport%20processing%20systems%20are%20performing%20without%20issues%2C%20with%20over%20two%20million%20applications%20already%20processed%20in%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20representative%20also%20added%20that%20they%20had%20contacted%20Basi%20and%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20and%20green%20booklets%20that%20say%20passport%20on%20them%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65223c326561dd877e741af2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20image%20of%20passports.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Garrard%20Beck%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20photo%20mix-up%20delayed%20Daya's%20passport%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20passport%20office%20advises%20booking%20trips%20after%20a%20passport%20has%20been%20issued%2C%20but%20Basi%20said%20she%20thought%20three%20months%20was%20enough%20time%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Forganisations%2Fhm-passport-office%2Fabout%2Fabout-our-services%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20government%20website%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20most%20are%20processed%20within%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasi%20said%20she%20sent%20Daya's%20documents%20to%20the%20Liverpool%20passport%20office%20on%20December%2022.%20Then%2C%20on%20January%204%2C%20she%20said%20she%20received%20an%20email%20confirming%20that%20they%20received%20the%20application%20and%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20three%20weeks%20went%20by%2C%20Basi%20said%20she%20remembers%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20panic.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20it%20was%20getting%20nearer%20and%20nearer%20to%20our%20date%20of%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasi%20said%20she%20called%20the%20UK%20government's%20office%2C%20and%20a%20worker%20advised%20her%20to%20apply%20and%20pay%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassport-wait-times-delays-3-months-summer-travel-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efast-tracked%20passport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20speeds%20up%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20was%20denied%20with%20no%20reasoning%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20day%2C%20Basi%20called%20for%20updates.%20Finally%2C%20with%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20until%20they%20left%20for%20Egypt%2C%20a%20worker%20had%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Basi%2C%20the%20worker%20pulled%20up%20the%20passport%2C%20which%20had%20an%20image%20of%20a%20different%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20guy%20on%20the%20phone%20says%2C%20'The%20picture%20in%20front%20of%20me%20is%20a%20child%20that%20looks%20much%20older%20than%203%2C'%26quot%3B%20Basi%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20confirming%20that%20her%20daughter%20looked%20like%20her%20age%2C%20Basi%20said%20the%20worker%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BDoes%20she%20have%20adult%20teeth%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20clear%20that%20the%20picture%20on%20Daya's%20passport%20wasn't%20Daya.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20of%20a%20child%20between%207%20and%2012%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20couldn't%20find%20the%20image%20sent%20with%20Daya's%20application%2C%20so%20Basi%20rushed%20to%20get%20a%20new%20photo%20sent%20to%20the%20passport%20office.%20Then%2C%20Basi%20said%20the%20passport%20office%20sent%20this%20second%20set%20to%20the%20wrong%20regional%20office.%20With%20the%20vacation%20quickly%20approaching%2C%20Basi%20mailed%20a%20third%20set%20of%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%2024%20hours%20before%20their%20flight%2C%20Basi%20said%20the%20family%20was%20informed%20the%20passport%20had%20been%20printed%20and%20was%20ready%20at%20the%20London%20office.%20She%20canceled%20work%2C%20took%20her%20daughter%20out%20of%20preschool%2C%20and%20drove%20to%20London%20to%20get%20the%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20time%2C%20Basi%20said%20this%20mishap%20cost%20her%20family%20more%20money%20than%20they%20initially%20planned%20with%20printing%20and%20mailing%20multiple%20sets%20of%20images.%20These%20costs%20come%20when%20the%20price%20of%20getting%20a%20UK%20passport%20continues%20to%20rise.%20This%20March%2C%20the%20UK%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fupdate-on-passport-application-fees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20that%20another%20cost%20increase%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20occur%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daya%20with%20her%20passport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fd8cca895d822030333e2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDaya%20with%20her%20passport.%3Cp%3EJasmeen%20Basi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ENow%2C%20Basi%20is%20left%20wondering%20where%20her%20daughter's%20pictures%20went%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20family%20left%20for%20Egypt%2C%20and%20while%20Basi%20is%20thrilled%20all%20four%20family%20members%20will%20be%20able%20to%20vacation%20together%2C%20she%20said%20it's%20still%20unsettling%20not%20knowing%20where%20Daya's%20image%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20issue%20is%20that%20they%20can't%20tell%20me%20where%20my%20daughter's%20picture%20is.%20They%20don't%20know%20if%20it's%20been%20attached%20to%20someone%20else's%20passport%20application.%20They%20can't%20locate%20the%20child%20whose%20photo%20was%20attached%20to%20my%20daughter's%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20data%20breach%20and%20where%20our%20child's%20picture%20is%2C%20they%20just%20can't%20tell%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasi%20said%20she%20had%20filed%20at%20least%20three%20complaints%20now%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20radio%20silence%20from%20the%20passport%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20anxiety-inducing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassport-office-lost-childs-photo-parent-says-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711374980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fd8e482417f97b87ce59d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassport-office-lost-childs-photo-parent-says-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jasmeen%20Basi%20said%20her%20daughter's%20passport%20was%20delayed%20because%20the%203-year-old's%20image%20had%20been%20accidentally%20replaced%20with%20a%20photo%20of%20an%20older%20child.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mhumphries%40businessinsider.com%20(Monica%20Humphries)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassport-office-lost-childs-photo-parent-says-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20this%20obsolete%20mechanism%20makes%20watches%20more%20expensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FfLyX3w56-jZbcmOYf.html%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%