20it.%20They%20hate%20that%20somebody%20within%20the%20fold%20is%20questioning%20them.%20This%20is%20not%20something%20that%20has%20been%20happening%20all%20this%20while.%20And%20him%20being%20a%20Brahmin%20man%20himself%20talking%20about%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20community%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20them.%20So%2C%20I%20totally%20understand%20that%20and%20I%20understand%20their%20anger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET.M.%20Krishna%20is%20not%20wrong%20because%20I%20have%20seen%20all%20of%20this.%20Because%20I%20have%20faced%20this%20thing%20being%20a%20dicorcee%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20and%20know%20how%20women%20are%20treated%20even%20if%20you%20are%20from%20the%20same%20community%20and%20%5Bhave%20to%20face%5D%20the%20misogyny%20and%20%5Bknow%5D%20how%20they%20speak%20of%20women%20performers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20of%20their%20garb%20of%20purity%2C%20devotion%20and%20bhakti%2C%20they%20are%20really%20rude%20and%20abusive%20and%20when%20someone%20says%20something%20they%20say%20what%20is%20your%20pedigree.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20had%20to%20unnecessarily%20keep%20saying%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20this%20pedigree%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20own%20grandfather%20%5BSripada%20Pinakapani%5D%20was%20a%20Sangita%C2%A0%20Kalanidhi%20and%20a%20Padma%20Bhushan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eso%20unless%20you%20throw%20weight%20around%20like%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20listen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20kind%20of%20calling%20out%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20if%20somebody%20else%20would%20have%20done%20the%20same%2C%20they%20would%20basically%20say%20you%20are%20just%20a%20playback%20singer%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhat%20do%20you%20know%20about%20Carnatic%20music.%20I%20have%20been%20trained%20in%20classical%20music%20and%20I%20have%20had%20%5Ba%5D%20government%20scholarship%20when%20I%20was%20a%20child%20and%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20prodigy%20and%20all%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BWith%20respect%20to%20Me%20Too%20allegation%5D%2C%20you%20look%20at%20the%20language%20and%20replies%20that%20they%20use.%20Some%20of%20them%20say%20that%20%E2%80%98she%20deserves%20this%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98I%20think%20we%20believe%20her%20molester%E2%80%99.%20How%20does%20somebody%20even%20try%20and%20talk%20common%20sense%20to%20this%20lot%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDo%20you%20think%20that%20Krishna%20is%20being%20attacked%20only%20because%20of%20his%20opinion%20on%20casteism%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20other%20reason%20which%20is%20forcing%20them%20to%20protest%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20beyond%20it.%20They%20are%20basically%20opposing%20the%20Sangita%C2%A0%20Kalanidhi%20%5Bconferred%20on%20Krishna%5D%20because%20of%20his%20efforts%20to%20call%20out%20the%20community.%20And%20he%20is%20a%20Periyar%20follower%20that%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20have%20to%20look%20at%20things%20with%20respect%20to%20context%20and%20time.%20Many%20things%20that%20somebody%20said%20in%20the%20past%20will%20not%20be%20applicable%20today.%20And%20Periyar%20was%20one%20person%20who%20constantly%20told%20people%20that%20even%20if%20I%20tell%20you%2C%20you%20are%20supposed%20to%20question%20even%20me%3B%20question%20yourself%20and%20question%20your%20beliefs.%20I%20would%20say%20he%20was%20someone%20who%20always%20spoke%20about%20rational%20and%20critical%20thinking.%20Critical%20thinking%20and%20questioning%20is%20not%20something%20that%20will%20be%20acceptable%20to%20bigoted%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeriyar%20is%20non-consequential%20at%20this%20point.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20have%20responded%20%5Bon%20X%5D%20saying%20Periyar%20is%20not%20the%20one%20getting%20the%20award%2C%20he%20is%20dead%2C%20so%20why%20does%20it%20matter%2C%20if%20somebody%20for%20instance%20if%20T.M.%20Krishna%20tomorrow%20converts%20to%20a%20different%20faith%20and%20if%20he%20is%20still%20a%20fantastic%20Carnatic%20classical%20musician%20then%20they%20will%20still%20argue%20saying%20that%20somebody%20who%20is%20not%20a%20Hindu%20should%20not%20get%20the%20award.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20it%20boils%20down%20to%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYou%20have%20also%20mentioned%20in%20your%20X%20handle%20that%20these%20are%20the%20same%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20did%20not%20speak%20out%20during%20%E2%80%98Me%20Too%E2%80%99.%20Why%20did%20you%20say%20so%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20people%20who%20are%20supporting%20Ranjini%20Gayatri%20are%20saying%20that%20I%20am%20a%20liar%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20that%20they%20have%20spoken%20%5Bagainst%20people%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%5D.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20they%20have%20spoken.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20that%20they%20did.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20who%20said%20what%20and%20if%20they%20said%20at%20all%2C%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20stand%20corrected%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20engagement%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20vehemence%20and%20%5Bthe%5D%20anger%20%5Bwith%20which%5D%20they%20are%20fighting%20for%20this%20cause%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%20then%20%5Bduring%20Me%20Too%5D.%20Someone%20is%20saying%20I%E2%80%99m%20returning%20the%20award.%20Please%20return%20quietly%20and%20go.%20Someone%20is%20saying%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20perform.%20Other%20people%20who%20will%20come%20and%20take%20your%20slot.%20So%20that%20is%20absolutely%20fine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcarnatic-music-academy-tm-krishna%5C%22%3ET.M.%20Krishna%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Richness%E2%80%99%20of%20Carnatic%20Ragas%20and%20the%20Music%20Akka-Demy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20this%20entire%20argument%20that%20T.M.%20Krishna%20cannot%20be%20awarded%20because%20he%20follows%20Periyar%20is%20why%20I%20said%20if%20you%20are%20actually%20a%20proper%20good%20human%20being%2C%20if%20you%20are%20going%20into%20this%20character%20%5Bassassination%5D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhat%20one%C2%A0%20is%20doing%20in%20their%20personal%20life%2C%20if%20one%20is%20drinking%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eif%20you%20are%20digging%20all%20this%20then%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20that%20you%20use%20the%20same%20yardstick%20for%20everybody%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20of%20this%2C%20the%20biggest%20joke%20is%20Ravikiran%20saying%20that%20I%20am%20returning%20my%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi.%20He%20is%20actually%20someone%20who%20was%20accused%20by%20his%20own%20students%20for%20molesting%20them.%20It%20should%20have%20been%20taken%20away%20from%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20it%20had%20been%20any%20smaller%2C%20less%20influential%20sort%20of%20a%20person%20without%20the%20clout%20that%20T.M.%20Krishna%20has%20today%2C%20they%20would%20have%20butchered%20and%20thrown%20apart%20%5Bthat%20person%5D.%20They%20are%20not%20able%20to%20touch%20T.M.%20Krishna%20because%20he%20himself%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20personal%20clout%20and%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20they%20can%20cry%20as%20they%20like%2C%20see%20how%20they%20are%20grouping%20together%20as%20a%20community%20to%20do%20this%20and%20this%20is%20what%20they%20will%20do%20against%C2%A0%20anybody%20who%20tries%20to%20raise%20a%20question.%C2%A0%20There%20are%20these%20kids%20who%20tried%20to%20form%20some%20sort%20of%20an%20ICC%20with%20proper%20accountability%2C%20actionable%20steps%20and%20all%20of%20that.%20So%2C%20because%20this%20Carnatic%20music%20community%20is%20very%20small%20they%20identified%20all%20of%20these%20students%20and%20kids%20who%20were%20doing%20this%20and%20they%20started%20blackisting%20them%20And%20decided%20not%20to%20give%20them%20any%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekutcheri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%20So%20basically%20they%20want%20to%20show%20that%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20stand%20up%20for%20the%20community%20then%20this%20is%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20you.%20This%20is%20how%20they%20treat%20kids%20who%20want%20to%20bring%20about%20any%20changes%20or%20get%20anything%20done%20and%20they%20have%20constantly%20stone%20walled%20the%20ICC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20only%20in%20this%20case%20that%20they%20have%20posted%20impatiently%20on%20social%20media%20and%20responded.%20Ranjini%20and%20Gayatri%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond%20to%20me%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time%20%5Bduring%20Me%20Too%5D%20in%202018%2C%20like%20they%20responded%20today.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERadha%20Ravi%20is%20the%20person%20who%20had%20banned%20me.%20He%20is%20in%20the%20BJP%20now.%20The%20person%20who%20molested%20me%20is%20Vairamuthu%2C%20who%20is%20constantly%20platformed%20by%20the%20DMK%2C%20heavy%20weights%20like%20Kamal%20Hassan%20and%20chief%20minister%20and%20everybody%20from%20the%20left%20wing.%20I%20and%2018%20other%20women%20named%20Vairamuthu%20as%20their%20molester.%20Vairamuthu%20paid%20nothing%2C%20I%20paid%20the%20price%2C%20and%20I%20got%20banned%20almost%20immediately%20and%20I%20have%20suffered%20because%20of%20that.%20I%E2%80%99m%20still%20fighting%20the%20case%20in%20the%20City%20Civil%20Court%20in%20Chennai.%20My%20case%20is%20sub-judice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20artists%20like%20Samantha%20%5BRuth%20Prabhu%5D%20and%20Parvathy%20%5BThiruvothuhave%5D%20have%20spoken%20up%20for%20me.%20My%20mother%20tongue%20is%20Tamil%20but%20I%20have%20sung%20in%20other%20languages%20like%20Telugu%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Marathi.%20I%20have%20won%20five%20Filmfare%20Awards%20so%20far%20and%204%20to%205%20state%20government%C2%A0%20awards.%20There%C2%A0%20are%20some%20people%20who%20have%20given%20me%20work%20post%E2%80%93Me%20Too%20like%20Govind%20Vasantha%2C%20but%20those%20are%20like%20two%20films%20a%20year%20or%20something%20like%20that%20while%20I%20was%20a%20pretty%20busy%20playback%20singer%20and%20dubbing%20artist%20prior%20to%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20had%20to%20pay%20a%20very%20heavy%20price%2C%20loss%20of%20career%2C%20opportunity%20and%20of%20course%20money%20because%20of%20this.%20So%20people%20keep%20saying%20that%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20and%20publicity%20because%20of%20the%20way%20I%20speak.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20to%20drive%20home%20the%20point%20that%20none%20of%20this%20attention%20and%20publicity%20is%20worth%20even%20one%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epaisa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20my%20bills%20nor%20does%20it%20get%20me%20work%20nor%20any%20attention%20that%20translates%20to%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDo%20you%20think%20that%20change%20is%20possible%20in%20the%20Carnatic%20music%20community%20now%20though%20you%20have%20clearly%20suggested%20that%20things%20haven%E2%80%99t%20changed%20much%20after%20Me%20Too%20in%20the%20industry%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20said%20and%20done%2C%20during%20the%20Me%20Too%20movement%20in%202018%2C%20the%20Music%20Academy%20had%20said%20that%20whoever%20was%20named%20in%20the%20movement%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20perform%20here%20%5Bin%20December%202018%5D.%20So%20that%20one%20year%20they%20made%20sure%20that%20they%20%5Bthose%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%5D%20don%E2%80%99t%20perform%20in%20the%20music%20academy.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20they%20have%20performed%20in%20consecutive%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5