0Rob%20Hobson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20keep%20eating%20more%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%20But%20there%20are%20minimally%20processed%2C%20healthier%20snacks%20at%20the%20store%20if%20you%20know%20what%20to%20look%20for%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHobson%20decided%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20UPFs%20partly%20because%20they%20are%20linked%20to%20health%20concerns%20such%20as%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20type%20two%20diabetes%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20cancer.%20They%20are%20also%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprocessed-food-makes-us-fat-leads-to-cancer-alternatives-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovereating%20and%20weight%20gain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20tend%20to%20contain%20lots%20of%20salt%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20saturated%20fats.%20Experts%20don't%20fully%20understand%20why%20processed%20foods%20are%20bad%20for%20our%20health%2C%20but%20the%20evidence%20suggesting%20that%20they%20are%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHobson%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fwhat-is-processed-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefines%20UPFs%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20items%20containing%20five%20or%20more%20ingredients%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20which%20you%20wouldn't%20find%20in%20a%20regular%20kitchen%20%E2%80%94%20that%20often%20have%20a%20long%20shelf%20life%20and%20come%20in%20highly%20marketed%20packaging.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20the%20minimally%20processed%20snacks%20he%20picks%20up%20from%20the%20store%20when%20he's%20hungry%20and%20in%20a%20rush%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFruit%20and%20nut%20bars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultra-processed-foods-marketed-as-healthy-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtein%20bars%3C%2Fa%3E%20tend%20to%20be%20ultra-processed%2C%20although%20they%20can%20certainly%20have%20their%20place%20in%20a%20balanced%20diet%20when%20eaten%20in%20moderation%2C%20dietitian%20Taylor%20Grasso%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20snack%20bars%20made%20with%20just%20dried%20fruit%20and%20nuts%20are%20a%20good%20minimally%20processed%20option%20that%20you%20can%20pick%20up%20from%20a%20store%2C%20Hobson%20said.%20Nuts%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20plant-based%20protein%20and%20contain%20heart-healthy%20fats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20a%20fan%20of%20British%20brand%20Nakd's%20bars%2C%20which%20can%20be%20bought%20online%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHummus%20and%20crudit%C3%A9s%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20healthy%20snack%20option%20is%20hummus%20paired%20with%20some%20chopped%20vegetables%2C%20such%20as%20carrot%20sticks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHummus%20contains%20chickpeas%2C%20a%20source%20of%20fiber%20and%20protein%2C%20and%20olive%20oil%2C%20which%20contains%20healthy%20fats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHobson%20recommended%20always%20looking%20at%20the%20nutritional%20label%20because%20some%20products%20contain%20fewer%20additives%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221254%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hummus.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d0250bb4cf2703e5b5aaecf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22836%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHummus%20and%20carrot%20sticks%20is%20a%20great%2C%20healthy%20snack.%20%3Cp%3Erobynmac%2FiStock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ENut%20butter%20and%20rice%20cakes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrab%20a%20jar%20or%20squeezy%20packet%20of%20nut%20butter%2C%20such%20as%20peanut%2C%20almond%2C%20or%20cashew%2C%20with%20as%20few%20ingredients%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20spread%20it%20on%20a%20rice%20cake%2C%20Hobson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20nice%20protein%20snack%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPlain%20popcorn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20be%20used%20to%20enjoying%20popcorn%20doused%20in%20salt%20and%20butter%20at%20the%20movie%20theatre%2C%20but%20if%20you%20eat%20it%20plain%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20healthy%20snack%2C%20Hobson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPopcorn%20is%20high%20in%20fiber%20and%20considered%20a%20whole%20grain%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20a%20reduced%20risk%20of%20diabetes%20and%20cardiovascular%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFresh%20fruit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20may%20sound%20obvious%2C%20fresh%20fruit%2C%20such%20as%20berries%2C%20oranges%2C%20and%20apples%2C%20is%20easy%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20eat%20on%20the%20go.%20You%20can't%20find%20a%20less%20processed%20snack%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminimally-processed-grocery-store-snacks-nutritionist-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711369134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fc60d4895d82203033010d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminimally-processed-grocery-store-snacks-nutritionist-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20trying%20curb%20ultra-processed%20foods%2C%20finding%20minimally%20processed%20grocery%20store%20snacks%20might%20be%20challenging.%20A%20nutritionist%20shares%20what%20he%20buys.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminimally-processed-grocery-store-snacks-nutritionist-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing's%20CEO%20announces%20he%20will%20resign%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20amid%20the%20Alaska%20Airlines%20safety%20saga%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boeing%20CEO%20Dave%20Calhoun%20is%20arriving%20for%20a%20meeting%20with%20Senator%20Tammy%20Duckworth%20(D-IL)%20in%20the%20Hart%20Senate%20Office%20Building%2C%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20on%20January