peaker-om-birla-in-kota-5307700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20kids%20have%20my%20maiden%20name%20as%20middle%20names.%20I%20wanted%20their%20names%20to%20honor%20my%20family%20legacy%2C%20not%20just%20their%20father's.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221398%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stephanie%20Claytor's%20kids%20holding%20hands%20and%20walking%20on%20a%20sidewalk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb44bc2417f97b87cde000%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStephanie%20Claytor's%20kids%20have%20her%20maiden%20name%20as%20their%20middle%20name.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Stephanie%20Claytor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI've%20never%20liked%20the%20tradition%20of%20automatically%20giving%20children%20their%20father's%20last%20name.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20wanted%20a%20way%20to%20incorporate%20my%20maiden%20name%20into%20my%20kids'%20names%20to%20preserve%20my%20family%20legacy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEven%20though%20my%20husband%20is%20very%20traditional%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20always%20known%20that%20the%20long-standing%20tradition%20in%20the%20United%20States%20was%20for%20children%20to%20be%20given%20only%20their%20father's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblended-last-names-after-marriage-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elast%20name%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20never%20liked%20it.%20It%20felt%20like%20an%20erasure%20of%20the%20mother's%20heritage%2C%20a%20way%20to%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20track%20her%20lineage%20and%20ancestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20thought%20it%20was%20fair%2C%20considering%20mothers%20carried%20and%20birthed%20the%20children.%20But%20I%20also%20didn't%20realize%20it%20wasn't%20a%20global%20norm%20until%20I%20saw%20my%20Puerto%20Rican%20friend's%20driver's%20license.%20I%20had%20only%20heard%20her%20use%20her%20father's%20last%20name%20when%20telling%20me%20her%20name%2C%20but%20upon%20looking%20at%20her%20driver's%20license%2C%20I%20realized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-didnt-change-my-last-name-after-marriage-how-its-going%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20legal%20name%3C%2Fa%3E%20included%20both%20her%20mother's%20and%20father's%20last%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifteen%20years%20after%20that%20experience%2C%20I%20was%20pregnant%20with%20my%20first%20child.%20I%20had%20married%20a%20southern%2C%20African%20American%20man%20who%20was%20very%20traditional%20in%20his%20way%20of%20thinking.%20I%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20had%20become%20accustomed%20to%20people%20having%20both%20their%20mother%20and%20father's%20last%20name%20by%20that%20point%20after%20my%20time%20living%20in%20Latin%20America.%20I%20knew%20I'd%20never%20be%20able%20to%20convince%20my%20husband%20to%20do%20this%2C%20but%20I%20still%20had%20a%20strong%20desire%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanged-last-name-husband-hyphenated-maiden-married-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincorporate%20my%20maiden%20name%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20our%20child's%20name%20somehow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20family%20history%20is%20important%20to%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why.%20The%20Claytors%20have%20a%20rich%20legacy.%20Our%20family%20history%20is%20detailed%20back%20to%20the%20Claytor%20plantation%20in%20a%201%2C000-page%20book%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd105291a4d8c96214fad6716f20d7ffd23ab1cead9b3c5facb94a5fd4010be44%26postID%3D65fb445a894bac29c429eba3%26postSlug%3Dkids-maiden-name-middle-names-family-legacy-2024-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FVirginia-kaleidoscope-Claytor-Kinships-Families%252Fdp%252FB0006QCKP6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Virginia%20Kaleidoscope%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Having%20this%20type%20of%20knowledge%20of%20family%20history%20is%20incredibly%20rare%20for%20an%20African%20American%20family.%20Our%20family%20has%20also%20had%20weekend-long%20family%20reunions%20every%20two%20years%20in%20hotels%20across%20the%20United%20States%20since%201976.%20I've%20never%20missed%20one.%20We%20give%20out%20%241%2C000%20scholarships%20to%20family%20members%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20includes%20people%20who%20are%20trailblazers%20in%20their%20fields%2C%20like%20my%20great%20grandfather's%20first%20cousin%2C%20William%20Schieffelin%20Claytor%2C%20who%20was%20the%20third%20African%20American%20to%20receive%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20mathematics%2C%20and%20my%20father%2C%20Darrell%20Claytor%2C%20a%20certified%20financial%20planner%20who%20was%20distinguished%20with%20a%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20in%202012.%20I've%20also%20made%20our%20last%20name%20pretty%20popular%20through%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blacktrekking.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20blog%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20television%20reporting%20career%20across%20the%20South%20and%20Midwest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20come%20from%20a%20long%20line%20of%20advocates%2C%20including%20my%20first%20cousin%2C%20Ifeolu%20Claytor%2C%20a%20city%20councilman%20who%20works%20to%20influence%20elections%20through%20%26quot%3BGet%20Out%20the%20Vote%2C%26quot%3B%20campaigns.%20Another%20one%20of%20my%20great-grandfather's%20first%20cousins%2C%20Dr.%20Walter%20Claytor%2C%20was%20a%20well-known%20dentist%20who%20successfully%20sued%20the%20Roanoke%20Redevelopment%20and%20Housing%20Authority%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20transformation%20of%20Virginia%20eminent%20domain%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20reading%20about%20our%20family's%20history%2C%20I%20learned%20I%20come%20from%20a%20long%20list%20of%20first-born%20sons%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20plantation.%20Only%20my%20great-grandfather%20was%20not%20firstborn.%20I'm%20the%20first%2C%20first-born%20girl%20in%20six%20generations