%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital%2C%20we%20finally%20came%20to%20an%20agreement%20on%20her%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compromise%3A%20I%20told%20my%20husband%20he%20didn't%20have%20to%20give%20me%20a%20push%20gift%20and%20I%20let%20him%20choose%20her%20first%20name%2C%20as%20it%20was%20a%20name%20that%20I%20liked%20as%20well.%20In%20exchange%2C%20I%20gave%20my%20daughter%20two%20middle%20names%2C%20the%20first%20name%20I%20originally%20wanted%20to%20name%20her%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-never-considered-changing-her-last-name-after-getting-married-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20maiden%20name%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Both%20children%20have%20my%20husband's%20last%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20already%20knows%20his%20full%20name%20and%20says%20it%20with%20joy.%20We%20will%20soon%20teach%20our%20daughter%20her%20full%20name%20as%20well.%20The%20kids%20will%20continue%20the%20tradition%20of%20going%20to%20my%20family%20reunions%20and%20bonding%20with%20my%20extended%20family.%20As%20they%20grow%20older%2C%20we'll%20read%20%26quot%3BThe%20Virginia%20Kaleidoscope%26quot%3B%20together%20and%20discover%20the%20achievements%20of%20my%20ancestors.%20While%20they%20may%20not%20often%20use%20their%20middle%20names%2C%20they'll%20understand%20why%20mommy%20was%20adamant%20about%20also%20passing%20down%20her%20maiden%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-maiden-name-middle-names-family-legacy-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711366441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb45d4895d82203032c6ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-maiden-name-middle-names-family-legacy-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20wanted%20my%20kids%20to%20have%20my%20maiden%20name%20to%20preserve%20my%20family%20legacy.%20My%20husband%20is