60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223466%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Chick-fil-A%20restaurant%3Cp%3EMichael%20Siluk%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChick-fil-A%20will%20start%20serving%20some%20chicken%20that%20has%20been%20raised%20with%20antibiotics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnder%20the%20new%20policy%2C%C2%A0animal%20antibiotics%20can%20be%20used%20if%20the%20chicken%20and%20those%20around%20it%20are%20sick.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChick-fil-A%20announced%20its%20No%20Antibiotics%20Ever%20policy%20in%202014%20and%20implemented%20it%20in%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-new-store-designs-photos-drive-thru-walk-up2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChick-fil-A%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20dropping%20its%20ban%20on%20serving%20chicken%20that%20has%20been%20raised%20with%20antibiotics%2C%2010%20years%20after%20first%20announcing%20the%20pledge%20and%20five%20years%20after%20it%20implemented%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20maintain%20supply%20of%20the%20high-quality%20chicken%20you%20expect%20from%20us%2C%20Chick-fil-A%20will%20shift%20from%20No%20Antibiotics%20Ever%20(NAE)%20to%20No%20Antibiotics%20Important%20To%20Human%20Medicine%20(NAIHM)%20starting%20in%20the%20Spring%20of%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chicken%20chain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20standards%2C%20Chick-fil-A%20said%20that%20chicken%20antibiotics%20could%20be%20used%2C%20but%20only%20if%20the%20chicken%20and%20those%20around%20it%20were%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20animal%20does%20become%20ill%2C%20it%20will%20be%20treated%20with%20antibiotics%20not%20intended%20for%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20Chick-fil-A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chick-fil-a.com%2Fcustomer-support%2Four-food%2Fquality-ingredients-and-sourcing%2Fdo-you-use-hormones-or-antibiotics-in-your-chicken%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIn%20accordance%20with%20FDA%20requirements%2C%20all%20antibiotics%20must%20be%20cleared%20from%20the%20chicken's%20system%20before%20it%20is%20considered%20available%20for%20the%20chicken%20supply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20approach%20%26quot%3Brestricts%20the%20use%20of%20those%20antibiotics%20that%20are%20important%20to%20human%20medicine%20and%20commonly%20used%20to%20treat%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Chick-fil-A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chick-fil-a.com%2Four-chicken-commitment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20will%20affect%20Chick-fil-A's%20restaurants%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20and%20Canada%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chick-fil-a.com%2Fcustomer-support%2Four-food%2Fquality-ingredients-and-sourcing%2Fwhy-is-chick-fil-a-moving-to-no-antibiotics-important-to-human-medicine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChick-fil-A%20previously%20banned%20all%20antibiotics%20in%20the%20raising%20of%20its%20chickens.%20It%20said%20it%20had%20implemented%20its%20No%20Antibiotics%20Ever%20policy%20in%20all%20its%20restaurants%20in%20May%202019%2C%20about%20five%20years%20after%20it%20announced%20the%20commitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fchickfila-antibiotics-chicken-8a7e863eac9b848bf6115b15af70830e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20AP%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Chick-fil-A%20had%20had%20concerns%20about%20its%20ability%20to%20acquire%20supplies%20of%20chicken%20that%20had%20been%20raised%20without%20antibiotics.%20Last%20year%2C%20Tyson%20Foods%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US'%20biggest%20chicken%20supplier%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fretail-consumer%2Ftyson-foods-drop-no-antibiotics-ever-label-some-chicken-products-wsj-2023-07-02%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20retreating%20from%20its%20No%20Antibiotics%20Ever%20pledge%20by%20reintroducing%20some%20antibiotics%20not%20important%20to%20human%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAtlanta-based%20Chick-fil-A%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chick-fil-a.com%2Fpress-room%2Fannouncing-chick-fil-a-79th-and-2nd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%203%2C000%20restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Puerto%20Rico%20and%20plans%20to%20expand%20into%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-drop-antibiotic-free-chicken-food-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711366119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601579216bde8d4ead1a097%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-drop-antibiotic-free-chicken-food-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chick-fil-A%20announced%20its%20No%20Antibiotics%20Ever%20policy%20in%202014%20and%20said%20it%20had%20achieved%20the%20goal%20in%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A58%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchick-fil-a-drop-antibiotic-free-chicken-food-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AAP%20launches%20'DP%20campaign'%20for%20'saving'%20Constitution%2C%20democracy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711365911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108767506%2Cimgsize-19522.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faap-launches-dp-campaign-for-saving-constitution-democracy%2Farticleshow%2F108767043.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%2