%20speech%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20asked%20the%20commission%20if%20Modi%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20answerable%20to%20the%20commission%20or%20the%20public%20at%20large%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20made%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20ECI%20on%20Friday%20(March%2022)%20to%20bring%20its%20attention%20to%20a%20speech%20Modi%20made%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20earlier%20that%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2024%2F03%2Fshri-modis-statement-invoking-religious-sentiments-in-tamil-nadu-violates-the-mcc%2F%5C%22%3Ecited%20Modi%20as%20reportedly%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEjVWk-HMER8%3Ffeature%3Dshared%26t%3D948%5C%22%3Eevent%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Hindus%20believe%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3Enari%20shakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ematru%20shakti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc%20made%20statements%20about%20destroying%20shakti%20and%20that%20these%20were%20insults%20to%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20its%20rally%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Shivaji%20Park%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98INDI%20Alliance%E2%80%99%20openly%20announced%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20destroy%20the%20shakti%20that%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20has%20faith%20in.%20Everyone%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20knows%20what%20shakti%20means%20in%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20a%20video%20of%20the%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20said%20that%20several%20temples%20devoted%20to%20goddesses%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20were%20the%20%E2%80%98shakti%20of%20this%20place%E2%80%99%20and%20said%20that%20in%20Hinduism%2C%20the%20term%20refers%20to%20matru%20shakti%20and%20nari%20shakti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98INDI%20Alliance%E2%80%99%20repeatedly%20and%20deliberately%20insult%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarma%20said%20that%20these%20statements%20violated%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20and%20urged%20the%20ECI%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Modi%20if%20the%20report%20he%20cited%20was%20found%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInvoking%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20by%20a%20political%20leader%20during%20elections%20brazenly%20violates%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20what%20has%20been%20reported%20is%20factually%20correct%2C%20the%20commission%20should%20act%20on%20this%20urgently%20and%20initiate%20deterrent%2C%20exemplary%20proceedings%20against%20the%20person%20making%20such%20a%20statement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarma%20had%20said%20in%20his%20March%2022%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20having%20received%20a%20response%20yet%2C%20Sarma%20asked%20the%20commission%20on%20Monday%20(March%2025)%20if%20it%20had%20chosen%20to%20act%20on%20his%20complaint%20and%20if%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cafraid%20to%20act%20independently%E2%80%9D%20for%20any%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20that%20each%20one%20of%20you%20is%20presently%20occupying%20the%20office%20of%20the%20commission%20as%20a%20result%20of%20selection%20predominantly%20made%20by%20the%20ruling%20political%20executive%2C%20does%20the%20commission%20as%20a%20collective%20body%20feel%20obligated%20not%20to%20cause%20any%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20political%20executive%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20also%20asked%20the%20three-member%20poll%20body%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-led-panel-appoints-ex-ias-officers-gyanesh-kumar-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-as-election-commissioners%5C%22%3Enew%20law%20on%20how%20election%20commissioners%20are%20appointed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20the%20commission%20must%20address%20his%20questions%20publicly%20and%20hoped%20it%20would%20%E2%80%9Cdispel%20any%20%E2%80%A6%20perception%E2%80%9D%20that%20it%20was%20unwilling%20to%20be%20apolitical%20and%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20letter%20from%20Monday%20is%20reproduced%20in%20full%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20enforces%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%2C%20which%20applies%20from%20when%20elections%20are%20announced%20and%20until%20results%20are%20declared.%20It%20seeks%20to%20regulate%20actions%20by%20governments%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20politicians%20to%20help%20keep%20elections%20free%20and%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20code%20is%20voluntary%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fmodel-code-of-conduct-meaning-9217638%2F%5C%22%3Ebut%20the%20ECI%20issues%20notices%20to%20those%20who%20violate%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sometimes%20enforces%20punitive%20action%20as%20per%20its%20special%20powers.%20Some%20actions%20the%20model%20code%20prohibits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fmodel-code-of-conduct-explained-when-in-force-guidelines-and-action-on-violations%2Farticle67957740.ece%5C%22%3Ealso%20happen%20to%20be%20banned%20by%20criminal%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20other%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fmcc%2F%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20its%20provisions%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20shall%20be%20no%20appeal%20to%20caste%20or%20communal%20feelings%20for%20securing%20votes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%5CnFormer%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShri%20Rajiv%20Kumar%3Cbr%3E%5CnChief%20Election%20Commissioner%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShri%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%3Cbr%3E%5CnElection%20Commissioner%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%3Cbr%3E%5CnElection%20Commissioner%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDear%20Dr%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%2C%20S%2FShri%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%2F%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20requested%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%2C%20vide%20my%20letter%20of%20March%2022nd%2C%202024%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2024%2F03%2Fshri-modis-statement-invoking-religious-sentiments-in-tamil-nadu-violates-the-mcc%2F%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2024%2F03%2Fshri-modis-statement-invoking-religious-sentiments-in-tamil-nadu-violates-the-mcc%2F%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20examine%20and%20act%20firmly%20on%20the%20statement%20reported%20to%20have%20been%20made%20by%20Shri%20Modi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20Coimbatore%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20recently%2C%20appealing%20to%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20voters%20in%20prima%20facie%20violation%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20tried%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20the%20Commission%20has%20acted%20at%20all%20on%20my%20complaint%20and%20whether%20any%20order%20has%20been%20passed%20on%20it%20but%2C%20to%20my%20anguish%20and%20disappointment%2C%20I%20have%20not%20come%20across%20any%20evidence%20of%20it.%20It%20looks%20as%20though%20the%20Commission%20has%20chosen%20not%20to%20act%20on%20my%20complaint%20for%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20I%20remind%20the%20Commission%20that%20as%20a%20citizen%20I%20am%20entitled%20to%20know%20the%20outcome%20of%20my%20complaint%20under%20Article%2019%20of%20the%20Constitution%3F%20Is%20not%20the%20Commission%20aware%20of%20its%20obligation%20to%20disclose%20the%20action%20taken%20on%20the%20complaint%20under%20Section%204%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20concerned%20citizen%20and%20a%20voter%20having%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20ensuing%20elections%2C%20I%20have%20the%20following%20questions%20for%20each%20one%20of%20the%20three%20Election%20Commissioners%20to%20consider%20and%20provide%20satisfactory%20answers%20for%20the%20public%20to%20see%20at%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20website%20and%20judge%20for%20themselves%20the%20impartiality%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20Commission%20as%20an%20authority%20set%20up%20under%20Article%20324%20of%20the%20Constitution%20mandated%20to%20conduct%20elections%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Does%20the%20Commission%20consider%20a%20political%20leader%20appealing%20to%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20voters%20to%20vote%20for%20his%2Fher%20party%20not%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20MCC%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Does%20the%20Commission%20think%20that%20a%20complaint%20made%20by%20an%20ordinary%20citizen-voter%20like%20me%20need%20not%20be%20acted%20upon%2C%20and%20that%20the%20concerns%20of%20ordinary%20voters%20could%20be%20readily%20ignored%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Does%20the%20Commission%20consider%20that%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20beyond%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20MCC%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20he%20is%20not%20answerable%20to%20the%20Commission%20or%20the%20public%20at%20large%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Is%20there%20one%20set%20of%20rules%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20for%20Shri%20Modi%20and%20another%20set%20of%20rules%20for%20all%20others%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Has%20the%20Commission%20chosen%20to%20act%20on%20my%20complaint%20cited%20or%20decided%20to%20ignore%20it%20altogether%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Whether%20the%20Commission%20has%20ascertained%20the%20facts%20relating%20to%20the%20complaint%20from%20independent%20sources%20and%20passed%20a%20speaking%20order%20on%20my%20complaint%3F%20If%20so%2C%20can%20the%20Commission%20make%20a%20public%20disclosure%20of%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Have%20there%20been%20any%20differences%20in%20thinking%20among%20the%20three%20individual%20Commissioners%20on%20the%20complaint%20in%20question%20and%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20Commission%20not%20making%20a%20public%20disclosure%20of%20the%20dissenting%20views%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20Considering%20that%20each%20one%20of%20you%20is%20presently%20occupying%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Commission%20as%20a%20result%20of%20selection%20predominantly%20made%20by%20the%20ruling%20political%20executive%2C%20does%20the%20Commission%20as%20a%20collective%20body%20feel%20obligated%20not%20to%20cause%20any%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20political%20executive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20Is%20the%20Commission%2C%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20afraid%20to%20act%20independently%20on%20my%20complaint%20to%20enforce%20the%20MCC%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Considering%20that%20the%20expenses%20incurred%20by%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Commission%20are%20met%20from%20the%20public%20exchequer%2C%20should%20not%20the%20Commission%20feel%20accountable%20to%20the%20public%20at%20large%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20pointed%20out%20by%20me%20time%20and%20again%2C%20the%20public%20at%20large%20repose%20trust%20in%20the%20Commission%20as%20an%20independent%20Constitutional%20authority%20and%20expect%20it%20to%20function%20in%20an%20entirely%20apolitical%20manner%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20conduct%20elections%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner.%20If%20the%20Commission%20displays%20any%20bias%20in%20favour%20of%20those%20influential%20in%20the%20ruling%20political%20executive%2C%20or%20any%20fear%20to%20act%20against%20them%2C%20the%20trust%20that%20the%20public%20repose%20in%20it%20is%20sure%20to%20get%20eroded%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20efficacy%20to%20function%20as%20a%20Constitutional%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20request%20the%20Commission%20members%20to%20meet%20specially%20to%20discuss%20the%20above%20questions%20and%20provide%20satisfactory%20answers%20to%20the%20public%20at%20large%2C%20failing%20which%2C%20I%20am%20afraid%2C%20that%20one%20would%20be%20constrained%20to%20infer%20that%20the%20Commission%20has%20no%20intention%20whatsoever%20to%20elevate%20itself%20to%20fulfill%20the%20mandate%20under%20Article%20324%20and%20act%20as%20an%20apolitical%2C%20independent%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20sincerely%20hope%20that%20the%20Commission%20would%20do%20everything%20to%20dispel%20any%20such%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegards%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYours%20sincerely%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%5CnVisakhapatnam%3Cbr%3E%5Cn25th%20March%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711365749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23221501%2FThe-Wire-50.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fis-election-commission-afraid-to-act-on-my-mcc-complaint-against-modi-former-bureaucrat-asks%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22E.A.S.%20Sarma%20had%20written%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20about%20statements%20Modi%20made%20on%20%E2%80%98shakti%E2%80%99%20during%20an%20event%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20last%20week%2C%20saying%20they%20may%20have%20violated%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%20He%20said%20he%20did%20not%20hear%20back%20from%20the%20commission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fis-election-commission-afraid-to-act-on-my-mcc-complaint-against-modi-former-bureaucrat-asks%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20sneak%20peek%20into%20Bachchans%20HOLI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711365693000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108767502%2Cimgsize-58128.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnavya-naveli-amitabh-bachchan-and-jaya-bachchan-revel-in-holi-celebrations-with-pichkaris-water-buckets-yummy-food-and-more-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F108767537.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108767537.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Big%20B%20took%20to%20his%20blog%20to%20reminisce%20about%20Holi%20memories%20at%20his%20house%20Prateeksha.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BGreetings%