3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgeorgian-ruling-partys-sway-over-election-commission-boosted-before-october-poll%2Famp_articleshow%2F108767288.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgeorgian-ruling-partys-sway-over-election-commission-boosted-before-october-poll%2Famp_articleshow%2F108767288.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Family%20Feud%20In%20Baramati%3F%20Potential%20Supriya%20Sule-Sunetra%20Pawar%20Battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Sharad%20Pawar%20vs%20Ajit%20Pawar%20throwdown%20-%20and%20the%20legal%20squabble%20for%20control%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20-%20has%20dominated%20Maharashtra%20politics%20for%20nearly%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20-%20with%20less%20than%20a%20month%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20the%20Pawar%20vs%20Pawar%20spat%20may%20have%20a%20secondary%20storyline%20in%20Baramati%20-%20the%20'sugar%20bowl%20of%20Maharashtra'%20-%20where%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20could%20face%20off%20against%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%2C%20Sunetra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaramati%20has%20been%20the%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Pawar%20family%20since%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20is%20a%20six-time%20MP%20from%20this%20area%2C%20including%20four%20times%20in%20a%20row%20from%201996%20to%202004.%20Crucially%2C%20the%201999%20and%202004%20wins%20came%20after%20he%20split%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20form%20the%20NCP%2C%20underlining%20the%20fact%20Baramati%20voters%20followed%20Mr%20Pawar%20away%20from%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202009%20Baramati%20-%20which%20has%20never%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20only%20four%20times%20since%201989%20for%20a%20non-Pawar%20Congress%20candidate%20-%20has%20been%20held%20by%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20who%20is%20bidding%20to%20become%20a%20four-time%20MP%20from%20the%20high-profile%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%20she%20swatted%20away%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20BJP's%20Kanchan%20Rahul%20Kul%2C%20picking%20up%20nearly%2053%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20and%20defeating%20her%20rival%20by%20more%20than%201.5%20lakh%20ballots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarking%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20win%20may%20not%20be%20quite%20as%20easy%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20continuing%20battle%20to%20go%20one-up%20on%20his%20uncle%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%20his%20eye%20set%20on%20the%20prestigious%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20Earlier%20this%20month%20his%20party%20nominated%20his%20wife%20to%20contest%20the%20seat.%20Mr%20Pawar%20would%20perhaps%20have%20been%20the%20preferred%20choice%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20would%20have%20had%20to%20resign%20had%20he%20won%20the%20parliamentary%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20desperate%20to%20win%20Baramati%20too%3B%20victory%20here%20will%20be%20a%20statement%20of%20intent%20against%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%2C%20of%20which%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20faction%20is%20a%20part.%20It%20will%20also%20boost%20the%20'mission%2045'%20goal%2C%20which%20is%20to%20win%2045%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20likely%20contenders%20found%20themselves%20face-to-face%20at%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%20in%20Baramati%2C%20where%20cordial%20greetings%20and%20a%20hug%20were%20exchanged.%20The%20temple%20has%20political%20significance%20as%20all%20Pawar%20family%20members%2C%20including%20Ajit%2C%20visit%20before%20launching%20their%20election%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ms%20Sule's%20camp%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20her%20father%20and%20NCP%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20Also%20campaigning%20for%20her%20is%20Rohit%20Pawar%2C%20her%20nephew%2C%20who%20last%20month%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20summons%20to%20Mr%20Pawar%2C%20a%20first-time%20MLA%2C%20have%20been%20slammed%20as%20politically%20motivated%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP.%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20who%20accompanied%20her%20nephew%20on%20the%20day%20of%20questioning%2C%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20(again)%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20like%20the%20ED%20to%20target%20rival%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Pawar%20has%20declared%20a%20wave%20of%20sympathy%20for%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20-%20triggered%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20breakaway%20and%20attacks%20on%20his%2083-year-old%20uncle%20-%20will%20ensure%20Ms%20Sule's%20win%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sule%20has%20refrained%20from%20direct%20attacks%20on%20her%20sister-in-law%2C%20but%20has%20launched%20a%20wave%20of%20attacks%20on%20the%20political%20coalition%20she%20represents%2C%20which%20is%20made%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20NCP%20faction%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Pawar%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20been%20active%20trying%20to%20establish%20a%20political%20presence%20in%20the%20rural%20heartlands%20of%20Baramati.%20Her%20days%20begin%20at%208%20am%20and%20include%20lengthy%20meetings%20with%20villagers%20to%20understand%20their%20concerns.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20she%20acknowledged%20her%20lower%20profile%20but%20said%20she%20remains%20committed%20to%20carving%20out%20her%20own%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20while%20that%20the%20Supriya%20Sule-Sunetra%20Pawar%20story%20unfolds%2C%20there%20is%20a%20potential%20twist%20in%20the%20tale.%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Vijay%20Shivtare%20has%20said%20he%20will%20contest%20the%20Baramati%20seat%20too%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20previous%20election%2C%20Mr%20Shivtare%20was%20a%20candidate%20from%20Purandar%20but%20lost%2C%20earning%20jibes%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20Mr%20Shiv