ll%20for%20Gujarat%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%20He%20swung%20the%20new%20ball%20and%20bowled%20it%20well%2C%20which%20was%20nothing%20new%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20to%20use%20the%20advantage%20of%20the%20new%20ball%20swinging%20along.%20When%20I%20look%20at%20the%20decision%20made%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20it%2C%20and%20we%20move%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Pollard%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20discussion%20turned%20to%20the%20logic%20behind%20Hardik%20coming%20in%20to%20bat%20at%20number%20seven%20Pollard%20said%20one%20can't%20attribute%20the%20decision%20to%20the%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20decision%20is%20made%20on%20full%20autonomy%2C%20so%20we%20can't%20say%20it%20is%20his%20decision.%20As%20a%20team%2C%20we%20have%20plans%3B%20we%20talk%20about%20setting%20entry%20points%20for%20batters.%20The%20top%20order%20batted%20deep%20into%20the%20game%2C%20and%20we%20also%20had%20two%20power%20hitters%20to%20go%20in%20the%20back%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsually%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20it%20over%20time%2C%20Tim%20(David)%20has%20finished%20games%20for%20us%2C%20and%20Hardik%20has%20done%20it%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20at%20any%20point%2C%20any%20one%20of%20them%20can%20resurrect%20the%20situation.%20It%20didn't%20happen%20tonight%2C%20so%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20chat%20about%20who%20should%20have%20gone%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20all%20of%20those%20things%20are%20in%20hindsight%2C%20and%20as%20a%20team%2C%20we%20make%20decisions%2C%20so%20let's%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20'Hardik%20made%20a%20decision%2C%20Hardik%20did%20this%2C%20Hardik%20did%20that'.%20We%20are%20a%20team.%20We%20make%20decisions%20collectively%20as%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20West%20Indian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPollard%20also%20threw%20his%20weight%20behind%20embattled%20opener%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20said%20he%20will%20come%20good%20in%20the%20coming%20matches%20as%20he%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%26quot%3B%20player%20within%20the%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20him%2C%20again%2C%20he%20did%20not%20score%20tonight%20so%2C%20we%20can%20look%20at%20all%20sorts%20of%20different%20things%2C%20but%20I%20said%20it's%20a%20long%20tournament%2C%20he%20is%20an%20experienced%20guy%20within%20our%20setup%20and%20we%20expect%20big%20things%20from%20Ishan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20in%20a%20good%20space%2C%20he%20has%20been%20practising%20well%20and%20has%20been%20doing%20fairly%20decently%2C%20so%20hopefully%20within%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20games%2C%20you%20can%20see%20great%20performances%20from%20him%20and%20all%20of%20you%20will%20continue%20to%20laud%20his%20brains%20when%20he%20does%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Pollard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20was%20dismissed%20for%20a%20duck%20by%20Azmatullah%20Omarzai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20players%2C%20including%20Punjab%20all-rounder%20Naman%20Dhir%2C%20made%20their%20Mumbai%20Indians%20debut%20in%20the%20team's%20opening%20fixture%20of%20IPL%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPollard%20was%20impressed%20with%20Dhir's%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20kudos%20go%20to%20the%20scouts%20and%20all%20the%20guys%20who%20work%20behind%20the%20scenes%20and%20continue%20to%20unearth%20all%20of%20these%20talents.%20He%20was%20on%20the%20radar.%20For%20us%2C%20he%20has%20been%20within%20our%20setup%20for%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20going%20to%20England%20and%20developing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20was%20something%20that%20we'd%20seen%20in%20that%20guy%2C%20and%20he%20came%20out%20and%20was%20very%20expressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20with%20the%20lofted%20shot%2C%20we%20are%20excited%20about%20these%20things%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20he%20had%20much%20more%20to%20offer.%20His%20calmness%2C%20even%20when%20we%20lost%20that%20first