2%3EFormer%20Telangana%20Cop%20Arrested%20For%20Tapping%20Opposition%20Leaders'%20Phones%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraneeth%20Rao%20was%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20and%20charged%20with%20developing%20profiles%20of%20unknown%20persons%20and%20monitoring%20their%20activity%20in%20an%20unauthorised%20manner%2C%20as%20well%20as%20destroying%20certain%20computer%20systems%20and%20data%20stored%20on%20electronic%20gadgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evidence%20was%20reportedly%20destroyed%20on%20orders%20from%20Prabhakar%20Rao%3B%20the%20order%20was%20allegedly%20given%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Congress%20beat%20the%20BRS%20in%20the%202023%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farrested-telangana-cop-said-he-destroyed-intel-on-his-boss-orders-sources-5238374%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArrested%20Telangana%20Cop%20Said%20He%20Destroyed%20Intel%20On%20Boss'%20Orders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20individuals%20whose%20devices%20were%20reportedly%20monitored%20include%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20and%20members%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20from%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao's%20BRS.%20There%20are%20also%20reports%20that%20Telugu%20actors%20and%20businessmen%20were%20monitored%20too%2C%20and%20that%20many%20of%20them%20were%20blackmailed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20over%20one%20lakh%20phone%20calls%20were%20tapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20has%20vowed%20action%20and%20labelled%20Mr%20Rao%20a%20%26quot%3Bpresent-day%20Qasim%20Rizi%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BElements%20of%20the%20conspiracy%20are%20still%20under%20investigation%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20to%20come%20out...%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20at%20least%2030%20police%20officers%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20investigated%20as%20this%20can%20of%20w