xploration%20began%3F%20What%20sparked%20your%20interest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENitish%20Shrimal%20%5BNS%5D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20village%20in%20a%20remote%20part%20of%20Rajasthan.%20My%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20many%20resources%20and%2C%20even%20in%202007%2C%20electricity%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20available.%20Recognising%20these%20challenges%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20step%20up%20to%20improve%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20life.%20It%20was%20during%20my%2010th%20grade%20that%20I%20read%20about%20renowned%20scientists%20like%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20who%20later%20became%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20and%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20program.%20Their%20stories%20were%20deeply%20inspiring.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20began%20reading%20about%20the%20Columbia%20accident%20and%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20Kalpana%20Chawla%2C%20further%20igniting%20my%20fascination%20with%20space.%20This%20eventually%20led%20me%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20formal%20paths%20to%20join%20space%20organisations%20like%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sure%20if%20I%20could%20ever%20get%20into%20ISRO.%20Back%20then%2C%20it%20was%20considered%20as%20prestigious%20and%20competitive%20as%20NASA%20or%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%2C%20with%20extremely%20challenging%20entrance%20exams.%20I%20diligently%20prepared%20for%20the%20IIT-JEE%20entrance%20exam.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20missed%20the%20qualifying%20mark%20by%20a%20single%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20also%20applied%20to%20a%20college%20called%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Space%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20which%20was%20a%20new%20college%20at%20that%20time.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20prestigious%20then%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20only%20college%20in%20India%20dedicated%20to%20space%20studies.%20I%20chose%20Aerospace%20Engineering%20and%20graduated%20in%202016.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20when%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20I%20faced%20a%20challenge%20because%20my%20primary%20language%20was%20Hindi%2C%20which%20is%20mostly%20spoken%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20India.%20But%20B.Tech%20and%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degrees%20in%20Engineering%20are%20usually%20taught%20in%20English%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20and%20interpret%20engineering%20concepts%20in%20English%20and%20that%20was%20a%20significant%20challenge.%20I%20overcame%20that%20challenge%20and%20am%20fluent%20in%20it%20now.%20That%20was%20a%20personal%20achievement%20for%20me%20at%20that%20time%2C%20being%20able%20to%20learn%20a%20foreign%20language%20and%20excel%20at%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20in%20my%20final%20year%20of%20the%20B.Tech%20program%2C%20I%20met%20Professor%20R.V.%20Ramanan%2C%20who%20became%20my%20mentor.%20He%20taught%20spaceflight%20mechanics%20and%20he%20was%20also%20a%20deputy%20project%20director%20in%20Chandrayaan-1%2C%20which%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Moon%20mission.%20I%20was%20very%20fortunate%20to%20learn%20the%20subject%20from%20such%20an%20expert.%20He%20was%20very%20humble%20and%20interactive%2C%20and%20he%20made%20sure%20that%20everyone%20in%20the%20class%20understood%20the%20material.%20He%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20move%20on%20to%20the%20next%20topic%20until%20even%20the%20student%20in%20the%20last%20row%20understood%20the%20problem%20and%20could%20solve%20it.%20I%20was%20very%20impressed%20with%20him%20so%20I%20requested%20him%20to%20be%20my%20supervisor%20and%20he%20agreed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20did%20my%20first%20internship%20on%20Sun%20synchronous%20polar%20orbit%20design%20at%20ISTRAC%20Bangalore%2C%20which%20is%20a%20tracking%20station%20for%20ISRO.%20The%20project%20that%20I%20also%20did%20was%20under%20Professor%20Ramanan%E2%80%99s%20guidance%20and%20it%20was%20on%20Earth%20re-entry%20trajectory%20optimisation%20using%20angle%20of%20attack%20modulation%20for%20a%20shift%20in%20landing%20site.%20So%2C%20suppose%20a%20spacecraft%20has%20to%20land%20on%20a%20particular%20landing%20site%2C%20but%20due%20to%20some%20reason%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20land%20on%20a%20different%20site%2C%20right%3F%20What%20changes%20would%20the%20spacecraft%20need%20to%20make%20in%20orbit%20at%20entry%20conditions%3F%20This%20was%20a%20fascinating%20project%2C%20and%20it%20sparked%20my%20interest%20in%20orbital%20mechanics.%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20my%20career%20in%20orbital%20mechanics.%20I%20was%20very%20passionate%20about%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20recruitment%20in%20ISRO%2C%20the%20centre%20is%20allocated%20randomly.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20allocated%20to%20the%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20System%20Centre%2C%20where%20all%20the%20work%20is%20about%20propulsion.%20I%20was%20a%20little%20disappointed%20at%20that%20time%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20field%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%2C%20but%20it%20was%20also%20a%20good%20time%20to%20reflect.%20As%20I%20started%20working%2C%20my%20interest%20in%20propulsion%20grew.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20working%20in%20this%20area%20for%20about%20eight%20years%20now.%20This%20experience%20taught%20me%20that%20whatever%20happens%20in%20life%2C%20happens%20for%20a%20reason%2C%20and%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20you%20get%20the%20subject%20you%20were%20initially%20interested%20in%20or%20not.%20We%20always%20adapt.%20It%E2%80%99s%20human%20nature%20to%20always%20adapt%2C%20even%20though%20it%20takes%20time%2C%20and%20you%20only%20realise%20it%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20my%20journey%20as%20a%20propulsion%20engineer%20at%20ISRO%20in%202016.%20After%20five%20years%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20change%20and%20new%20career%20opportunities.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20saw%20a%20post%20from%20one%20of%20my%20colleagues%20that%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20keep%20calm%2C%20I%20was%20chosen%20for%20Chevening!%E2%80%9D%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20motto%20of%20the%20Chevening%20scholarship%2C%20and%20it%20sparked%20my%20curiosity.%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%20about%20it.%20When%20I%20found%20out%20that%20the%20Chevening%20scholarship%20was%20a%20fully%20funded%20scholarship%20for%20all%20Commonwealth%20country%20professionals%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20it%2C%20and%20I%20got%20it!%20It%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work.%20The%20application%20process%20is%20a%20year%20long%2C%20and%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20at%20your%20best%20at%20any%20stage%2C%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20get%20it.%20If%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20gotten%20it%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20able%20to%20pursue%20a%20Master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%20on%20my%20own%20financial%20resources%2C%20so%20this%20was%20a%20much-needed%20scholarship.%20Once%20I%20secured%20it%2C%20I%20was%20over%20the%20moon%2C%20and%20I%20told%20myself%20that%20I%20had%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20this%20one%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20participated%20in%20all%20sorts%20of%20activities%2C%20including%20volunteering.%20I%20participated%20in%20many%20university%20activities%20and%20even%20received%20the%20Employability%20award%20because%20I%20spent%20over%20100%20hours%20in%20workshops%20and%20volunteering%20activities.%20I%20also%20enrolled%20in%20an%20additional%20module%2C%20the%20Global%20Graduate%20Award%3A%20Introduction%20to%20Sustainability.%20In%20addition%20to%20my%20courses%2C%20I%20volunteered%20for%20One%20Young%20World%2C%20which%20was%20held%20in%20Manchester%20that%20year.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20this%20year%20because%20it%20was%20a%20hard-earned%20opportunity%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20excel%20in%20it.%20I%20also%20knew%20this%20incredible%20opportunity%20allowed%20me%20to%20travel.%20I%20came%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20immerse%20myself%20in%20the%20culture%2C%20particularly%20the%20space%20culture.%20I%20visited%20Glasgow%20and%2C%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20my%20stay%2C%20ventured%20into%20Europe%2C%20visiting%20Pisa%20and%20Milan%20before%20returning%20to%20re-join%20ISRO.%20After%20my%20return%2C%20I%20was%20awarded%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20on%20Chandrayaan%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20The%20Chevening%20scholarship%20application%20process%20coincided%20with%20recruitment%20for%20New%20Space%20India%20Limited%20(NSIL).%20You%20were%20offered%20a%20position%20at%20NSIL%20but%20declined%2C%20even%20before%20knowing%20the%20scholarship%20outcome.%20This%20suggests%20it%20held%20great%20importance.%20Why%20was%20traveling%20to%20the%20UK%20and%20gaining%20that%20experience%20so%20crucial%20for%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20saw%20the%20New%20Space%20India%20Limited%20(NSIL)%20interview%20as%20a%20practice%20run.%20My%20primary%20goal%20was%20Chevening.%20Success%20at%20NSIL%20would%20boost%20my%20confidence%20for%20Chevening.%20However%2C%20once%20I%20got%20an%20offer%20letter%20from%20NSIL%20Deputy%20Manager%20post%2C%20I%20became%20interested%20in%20NSIL%E2%80%99s%20mission%20to%20privatise%20India%E2%80%99s%20space%20sector.%20The%20position%20as%20a%20deputy%20manager%2C%20one%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20initial%20members%2C%20was%20very%20appealing.%20However%2C%20I%20had%20to%20decline%20as%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20further%20studies%20within%20the%20first%20four%20to%20five%20years%2C%20and%20pursuing%20studies%20was%20a%20strong%20personal%20desire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20my%20background%20is%20in%20aerospace%20engineering%2C%20with%20five%20years%20of%20propulsion%20experience%2C%20I%20lacked%20a%20holistic%20understanding%20of%20spacecraft%20operations.%20Other%20subsystems%20like%20thermal%2C%20AGNC%2C%20AOCS%20and%20Spacecraft%20Structures%20remained%20unfamiliar.%20Acquiring%20this%20knowledge%20would%20be%20advantageous%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20especially%20for%20future%20leadership%20roles%20in%20ISRO%2C%20where%20understanding%20how%20all%20subsystems%20interact%20is%20crucial.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThankfully%2C%20the%20one-year%20Master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20program%20allowed%20the%20organisation%20to%20grant%20me%20leave.%20While%20a%20two-year%20program%2C%20more%20common%20in%20India%20and%20other%20countries%2C%20would%20have%20been%20challenging%20to%20pursue%2C%20the%20one-year%20format%20aligned%20with%20my%20availability%20perfectly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Additionally%2C%20I%20harboured%20personal%20interests.%20As%20a%20cricket%20enthusiast%2C%20the%20scholarship%20presented%20an%20opportunity%20to%20visit%20Lord%E2%80%99s%2C%20the%20Mecca%20of%20cricket%2C%20and%20participate%20in%20related%20activities.%20Visiting%20filming%20locations%20for%20the%20Harry%20Potter%20series%20and%20%3Cem%3EGame%20of%20Thrones%3C%2Fem%3E%20brought%20me%20immense%20personal%20pleasure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20packed%20a%20lot%20into%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20never%20compromised%20my%20studies.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20received%20the%20Cable%20%26amp%3B%20Wireless%20Award%20for%20Best%20Overall%20Performance%20in%20my%20cohort%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey.%20Balancing%20it%20all%20required%20discipline%20and%20dedication%20but%20it%20was%20crucial%20to%20satisfy%20my%20cultural%20curiosity%20and%20experience%20this%20new%20world%20while%20still%20excelling%20in%20my%20studies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20You%20juggle%20a%20lot%2C%20balancing%20your%20current%20work%20at%20ISRO%2C%20your%20education%20and%20even%20a%20scholarship.%20Could%20you%20tell%20me%20about%20your%20concept%20of%20hard%20work%3F%20What%20role%20does%20it%20play%20in%20your%20life%20and%20how%20do%20you%20define%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20college%2C%20I%20came%20across%20the%20idea%20that%20with%20AI%20and%20other%20advancements%2C%20%E2%80%9Csmart%20hard%20work%E2%80%9D%20would%20replace%20hard%20work%20as%20the%20key%20to%20success%20in%20the%20future.%20I%20embraced%20that%20notion%20and%20believed%20it%20for%20a%20while.%20However%2C%20joining%20ISRO%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20smart%20hard%20work%20can%20sometimes%20lead%20to%20skipping%20crucial%20steps%20in%20the%20process.%20You%20jump%20from%20point%20A%20to%20point%20B%2C%20but%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20valuable%20learning%20in%20between.%20True%20success%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20discovered%2C%20lies%20in%20embracing%20the%20%E2%80%9Creal%20hard%20work%E2%80%9D%20that%20involves%20going%20through%20the%20entire%20process.%20This%20approach%20has%20yielded%20far%20more%20knowledge%20than%20shortcuts%20ever%20could.%20So%2C%20for%20me%2C%20hard%20work%20means%20fully%20engaging%20with%20the%20process%2C%20not%20finding%20ways%20to%20circumvent%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20What%20motivates%20you%20in%20your%20current%20work%20as%20a%20space%20propulsion%20engineer%3F%20Who%20or%20what%20are%20you%20working%20for%3F%20What%20is%20your%20mission%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20I%20enjoy%20my%20current%20position%2C%20I%20have%20a%20strong%20desire%20to%20share%20the%20knowledge%20I%E2%80%99ve%20gained.%20Coming%20from%20a%20humble%20background%2C%20I%20understand%20how%20unaware%20many%20people%2C%20especially%20in%20my%20village%2C%20are%20about%20space%20technology%20and%20its%20potential%20benefits%20for%20humanity.%20Just%20as%20I%20once%20struggled%20to%20navigate%20the%20path%20to%20ISRO%2C%20I%20see%20a%20gap%20in%20knowledge%20and%20accessibility%20that%20needs%20bridging.%20On%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20I%20try%20to%20connect%20with%20college%20students%20by%20offering%20career%20guidance%2C%20participating%20in%20podcasts%20and%20webinars%20(including%20some%20introductory%20sessions%20on%20rocket%20propulsion)%2C%20and%20starting%20with%20basic%20principles%20like%20how%20a%20balloon%20flies%2C%20to%20spark%20curiosity%20in%20young%20minds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20my%20search%20for%20a%20scholarship%2C%20I%20came%20across%20various%20options%20like%20the%20Chevening%20Fulbright%20and%20DAAD.%20Inspired%20to%20help%20others%2C%20I%20created%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20called%20%E2%80%98Your%20Scholar%20Guide%E2%80%99%20to%20offer%20insights%20and%20guidance%20on%20scholarship%20opportunities.%20The%20channel%20received%20positive%20feedback%20and%20gained%20over%201%2C500%20subscribers%20within%20six%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20challenge%20I%20faced%20was%20obtaining%20an%20Academic%20Technology%20Approval%20Scheme%20(ATAS)%20certificate%20for%20studying%20in%20the%20UK.%20This%20certificate%2C%20required%20for%20certain%20courses%20with%20potential%20misuse%20of%20sensitive%20technology%2C%20delayed%20my%20progress%20due%20to%20processing%20time%20and%20restrictions%20on%20specific%20keywords.%20Originally%20applying%20for%20Space%20Engineering%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20I%20had%20to%20switch%20to%20Satellite%20Communication%20Engineering%20within%20a%20short%20timeframe.%20Convincing%20both%20the%20Chevening%20scholarship%20committee%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%20required%20additional%20effort.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20highlighted%20a%20common%20issue%20faced%20by%20international%20students%20seeking%20ATAS%20certificates%2C%20which%20often%20leads%20to%20delays%20and%20confusion.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20I%20created%20a%20video%20explaining%20the%20application%20process%2C%20which%20gained%20significant%20views.%20While%20currently%20inactive%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20resume%20this%20initiative%20once%20I%20have%20more%20time%20from%20my%20professional%20commitments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20As%20an%20alumnus%20of%20both%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Space%20Science%20and%20Technology%20and%20the%20Chevening%20scholarship%20program%2C%20you%20have%20access%20to%20some%20impressive%20alumni%20networks.%20Many%20in%20the%20Indian%20space%20industry%20have%20spoken%20about%20the%20crucial%20role%20these%20networks%20play%20in%20their%20careers.%20Could%20you%20share%20your%20experience%20and%20highlight%20their%20importance%20to%20you%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%20Networking%20undeniably%20plays%20a%20major%20role%20in%20shaping%20career%20trajectories.%20In%20fact%2C%20my%20professional%20network%20began%20with%20Professor%20Ramanan%2C%20who%20generously%20provided%20crucial%20reference%20letters%20for%20my%20Chevening%20application.%20His%20support%20made%20a%20significant%20difference.%20He%20also%20connected%20me%20with%20Meg%20Bhatnagar%2C%20a%20senior%20alumnus%20with%20coding%20expertise%2C%20who%20helped%20me%20overcome%20a%20challenge%20with%20my%20Earth%20re-entry%20trajectory%20optimization%20problem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20within%20my%20first%20batch%20at%20IIST%2C%20Vasu%2C%20a%20senior%20I%20met%20during%20an%20interaction%20at%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Centre%2C%20shared%20his%20experience%20as%20the%20first%20Chevening%20scholar%20there.%20He%20graciously%20explained%20the%20application%20process%20and%20guided%20me%20through%20it.%20This%20reinforced%20an%20important%20lesson%3A%20having%20someone%20available%20to%20answer%20questions%20and%20offer%20support%20makes%20reaching%20any%20goal%2C%20be%20it%20a%20scholarship%2C%20job%20or%20another%20aspiration%2C%20considerably%20smoother.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20having%20a%20lifeline%20in%20a%20challenging%20sea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMentorship%20is%20equally%20vital%2C%20regardless%20of%20career%20stage.%20Networking%20provided%20me%20with%20invaluable%20mentorship%20at%20various%20points%20in%20my%20journey%3A%20securing%20employment%20at%20ISRO%2C%20embarking%20on%20the%20Chevening%20scholarship%2C%20and%20now%20exploring%20opportunities%20in%20Europe%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Professor%20Andrea%20Lucca%2C%20my%20former%20supervisor%20at%20Surrey%2C%20who%20will%20be%20a%20referee%20for%20me%20based%20on%20his%20familiarity%20with%20my%20work.%20Essentially%2C%20networking%20offers%20continuous%20support%20and%20opens%20doors%20throughout%20your%20career.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20currently%2C%20I%20actively%20engage%20with%20the%20CEO%20of%20Skyroot%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20private%20Space%20Company%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20ongoing%20benefits%20of%20networking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20After%20graduating%2C%20you%20interned%20at%20ISRO.%20Reflecting%20on%20your%20first%20interactions%20there%2C%20what%20were%20your%20initial%20impressions%20of%20the%20organization%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20a%20student%2C%20I%20perceived%20ISRO%20as%20heavily%20guarded%2C%20which%20is%20understandable%20for%20any%20institute%20of%20its%20kind.%20While%20you%E2%80%99re%20inside%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20it%2C%20but%20as%20an%20outsider%2C%20the%20security%20measures%20are%20evident.%20However%2C%20the%20people%20were%20friendly.%20During%20my%20bachelors%20internship%2C%20my%20guide%20at%20ISTRAC%2C%20Padma%20Dev%20Mishra%2C%20guided%20my%20friend%20and%20me%20throughout%20the%20project.%20He%20explained%20everything%20clearly%20and%2C%20being%20enthusiastic%20students%2C%20we%20completed%20the%20work%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20take%20us%20six%20months%20in%20just%20a%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20I%20worked%20on%20the%20Chandrayaan%203%20project%20and%20had%20to%20visit%20ISTRAC%2C%20the%20same%20centre%20for%20tracking%20propulsion%20performance%20of%20spacecraft%2C%20I%20met%20Mr.%20Mishra%20again.%20He%20had%20grown%20into%20a%20leadership%20position%20by%20then.%20Despite%20the%20seven-year%20gap%2C%20he%20recognised%20me%20and%20fondly%20recalled%20our%20collaboration.%20In%20fact%2C%20on%20the%20day%20Chandrayaan%203%20landed%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%20I%20saw%20him%20commentating%20on%20the%20mission%20live%20on%20television.%20It%20was%20surreal%20to%20remember%20him%20as%20my%20guide%20and%20witness%20his%20professional%20journey.%20I%20captured%20a%20screenshot%20of%20him%20on%20TV%20and%20shared%20it%20on%20my%20WhatsApp%20status%2C%20highlighting%20how%20the%20person%20I%20once%20worked%20with%20was%20now%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20mission.%20Such%20serendipitous%20connections%20bring%20little%20joys%20to%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20You%E2%80%99ve%20likely%20encountered%20the%20American%20perspective%20on%20space%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfinal%20frontier%2C%E2%80%9D%20implying%20a%20need%20for%20conquest.%20Some%20contend%20this%20view%20is%20ethnocentric.%20Could%20you%20share%20your%20perspective%20on%20this%20metaphor%20and%20how%20you%20envision%20outer%20space%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unlike%20conquering%2C%20I%20see%20space%20exploration%20as%20a%20shared%20endeavour%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20humanity.%20India%E2%80%99s%20space%20program%20has%20primarily%20focused%20on%20development%20and%20growth%2C%20providing%20crucial%20telecommunication%20infrastructure%20that%20has%20significantly%20boosted%20our%20education%20and%20IT%20sectors.%20Space%20activities%20also%20support%20disaster%20management%2C%20minimizing%20losses%20during%20cyclones%2C%20for%20example.%20These%20are%20valuable%20by-products%20of%20exploration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20an%20Indian%20perspective%2C%20I%20believe%20in%20harmony%20and%20collective%20well-being.%20Space%20exploration%20should%20serve%20these%20values.%20Of%20course%2C%20understanding%20our%20place%20in%20the%20universe%2C%20searching%20for%20potential%20life%20elsewhere%2C%20and%20pursuing%20lunar%20and%20Martian%20missions%20are%20all%20important%20endeavours.%20However%2C%20I%20stand%20against%20a%20competitive%20space%20race.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20How%20do%20you%20envision%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20international%20space%20sector%3F%20What%20are%20its%20strengths%20and%20how%20can%20it%20contribute%20more%20significantly%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Recent%20surveys%20indicate%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20the%20global%20space%20economy%20stands%20at%20merely%203%25%2C%20highlighting%20our%20immense%20potential%20in%20this%20arena.%20Our%20young%20population%2C%20with%2060-70%25%20falling%20between%2030%20and%2040%20years%20old%2C%20represents%20a%20significant%20strength.%20However%2C%20proper%20guidance%20and%20a%20well-defined%20path%20are%20crucial.%20The%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan%203%20has%20instilled%20a%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20can%20do%20it%E2%80%9D%20within%20ISRO%20and%20the%20nation.%20While%20the%20Chandrayaan%202%20setback%20raised%20doubts%2C%20Chandrayaan%203%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20has%20bolstered%20my%20personal%20confidence%20in%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20capabilities%20as%20well.%20As%20an%20expert%20in%20my%20specific%20subsystem%2C%20witnessing%20such%20collective%20success%20strengthens%20my%20trust%20in%20the%20team.%20The%20ongoing%20lunar%20and%20Aditya%20missions%20further%20fuel%20our%20aspirations%20for%20space%20exploration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20leading%20force%20in%20space%20programs%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20planned%20Chandrayaan%204%20sample%20return%20mission.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20XPoSat%20mission%2C%20a%20collaborative%20effort%20between%20NASA%20and%20ISRO%2C%20launched%20on%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%20demonstrates%20our%20growing%20international%20partnerships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20Your%20long-term%20ambition%20was%20to%20establish%20your%20own%20space%20company%20in%20India.%20Does%20this%20aspiration%20remain%20your%20ultimate%20goal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely%2C%20I%20still%20harbour%20that%20ambition%2C%20but%20my%20timeline%20has%20shifted.%20While%20two%20years%20ago%20I%20envisioned%20starting%20the%20company%20within%20six%20or%20seven%20years%2C%20I%20now%20believe%20that%20additional%20expertise%20and%20knowledge%20are%20key%20before%20embarking%20on%20this%20venture.%20My%20current%20goal%20is%20to%20gain%20further%20experience%20in%20the%20European%20or%20UK%20space%20sectors%2C%20potentially%20accompanied%20by%20a%20Master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20business.%20I%20also%20have%20specific%20interests%20in%20demonstrating%20green%20propulsion%20technology%20and%20its%20potential%20role%20in%20spacecraft%20reusability.%20Establishing%20my%20own%20company%20remains%20a%20long-term%20objective%2C%20and%20although%20the%20timeframe%20has%20adjusted%2C%20the%20fundamental%20goal%20endures%20as%20my%20career%20path%20unfolds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20What%20sparked%20your%20interest%20in%20green%20propulsion%3F%20What%20drives%20you%20to%20pursue%20this%20particular%20ambition%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20resources%20are%20rapidly%20depleting.%20Conventional%20space%20and%20launch%20vehicle%20propellants%20like%20monomethyl%20hydrazine%20and%20N2O4%20pose%20significant%20health%20and%20environmental%20risks.%20They%E2%80%99re%20carcinogenic%2C%20require%20extensive%20safety%20measures%2C%20and%20raise%20launch%20costs.%20My%20goal%20is%20to%20develop%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%E2%80%9D%20propellants%20that%20are%20safer%20to%20handle%2C%20have%20no%20adverse%20health%20effects%2C%20and%20minimize%20environmental%20impact.%20Achieving%20these%20three%20goals%20would%20benefit%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20potentially%20reduce%20costs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20Some%20prominent%20ISRO%20leaders%2C%20like%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20were%20known%20for%20their%20spiritual%20inclinations%20and%20philosophical%20views%20on%20space%20exploration.%20The%20current%20chairman%20has%20also%20been%20seen%20visiting%20temples%20before%20crucial%20launches.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20the%20relationship%20between%20spirituality%20and%20space%20exploration%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20see%20them%20as%20distinct%20realms.%20One%20pertains%20to%20inner%20peace%20and%20mental%20well-being%2C%20the%20other%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20professional%20domain.%20Good%20mental%20health%20can%20undoubtedly%20enhance%20performance%20in%20any%20profession%2C%20including%20space%20exploration.%20However%2C%20I%20believe%20they%20remain%20separate%20aspects.%20Inner%20peace%20can%20benefit%20various%20aspects%20of%20life%2C%20from%20personal%20relationships%20and%20finances%20to%20hobbies%20and%20networking.%20While%20someone%20might%20be%20spiritual%20and%20not%20interested%20in%20space%2C%20or%20vice%20versa%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20an%20inherent%20connection%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20Some%20perceive%20a%20contradiction%20between%20being%20a%20scientist%20and%20having%20spiritual%20beliefs%20in%20a%20higher%20power.%20You%2C%20however%2C%20view%20them%20as%20complementary.%20Is%20that%20accurate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%20They%20can%20be%20complementary%2C%20and%20managing%20them%20effectively%20is%20crucial.%20In%20trajectory%20design%2C%20we%20model%20potential%20errors%20caused%20by%20lunar%20gravity%2C%20solar%20perturbations%2C%20and%20atmospheric%20drag.%20However%2C%20for%20low-altitude%20targets%2C%20pinpointing%20these%20errors%20with%20absolute%20accuracy%20is%20impossible.%20There%20will%20always%20be%20some%20margin%20of%20error.%20In%20those%20instances%2C%20I%20believe%20in%20a%20higher%20power%20that%20minimizes%20these%20uncontrollable%20factors.%20While%20our%20current%20technology%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20offer%20a%20fully%20accurate%20model%20of%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20gravity%2C%20we%20do%20our%20job%20diligently%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20higher%20dimension%20at%20play%20that%20ultimately%20guides%20things%20towards%20the%20right%20outcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAS%3A%20To%20conclude%2C%20would%20you%20personally%20cherish%20the%20opportunity%20to%20travel%20to%20space%2C%20perhaps%20to%20the%20Moon%20or%20Mars%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely!%20Witnessing%20astronauts%20perform%20spacewalks%20or%20journey%20to%20space%20stations%20always%20sparks%20wonder%20in%20me.%20The%20sheer%20thrill%20of%20observing%20Earth%20from%20outer%20space%2C%20appreciating%20its%20beauty%20and%20acknowledging%20it%20as%20our%20sole%20home%20in%20this%20vast%20universe%2C%20would%20be%20unparalleled.%20If%20possible%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20limit%20myself%20to%20the%20Moon%20%E2%80%93%20both%20Mars%20and%20beyond%20beckon%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711359040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F04122047%2Fsatellite-67718_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Fa-young-boys-journey-from-remote-rajasthan-to-becoming-a-scientist-at-isro%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2