al%20that%20is%20meant%20to%20break%20fast%20during%20Ramzan%2C%20by%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20month-long%20Ramzan%20observance%20and%20fast-breaking%20festivities%20in%20Malerkotla%20are%20unique%20as%20they%20are%20not%20confined%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20There%20is%20iftar%20in%20Hindu%20temples%20and%20Gurdwaras.%20Muslims%20too%20have%20been%20inviting%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Christians%2C%20and%20members%20of%20other%20religious%20communities%20to%20join%20them%20in%20special%20Ramzan%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20erstwhile%20princely%20state%2C%20Malerkotla%20was%20founded%20by%20a%20ruler%20from%20present-day%20Afghanistan%2C%20Sheikh%20Sadruddin-i-Jahan%2C%20in%201454.%20Malerkotla%20was%20upgraded%20to%20the%2023rd%20district%20of%20Punjab%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20Captain%20Amarinder%20Singh%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20iftar%20and%20Ramzan%20prayers%20are%20being%20organised%20in%20gurdwaras%20almost%20every%20day.%20The%20president%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Brahmin%20Front%2C%20Mahant%20Swaroop%20Bihari%20Sharma%2C%20said%20they%20have%20been%20celebrating%20Roza%20Iftar%20and%20Eid%20here%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeither%20have%20we%20ever%20cared%20for%20the%20communal%20ideology%20of%20politicians%20nor%20would%20we%20let%20them%20preach%20to%20us.%20We%2C%20the%20Hindus%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20Christians%20have%20been%20together%20for%20ages%20in%20Malerkotla.%20There%20are%20politicians%20who%20try%20to%20incite%20violence%20but%20no%20religion%20teaches%20hatred.%20Nobody%20wants%20to%20fight.%20I%20keep%20telling%20people%20that%20before%20they%20talk%20about%20religion%2C%20let%20us%20become%20humans%20first.%20We%20should%20celebrate%20all%20festivals%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Laxmi%20Narayan%20Mandir%20and%20Aqsa%20Mosque%20are%20situated%20adjacent%20to%20each%20other%20in%20the%20Hindu-majority%20Somsons%20Colony%20at%20Malerkotla.%20The%20temple%20and%20the%20mosque%20share%20a%20common%20wall%2C%20reflecting%20deep%20ties%20dating%20back%20to%20over%20three%20centuries%2C%20said%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20pride%20in%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99s%20rich%20culture%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Shree%20Ram%20Mandir%20Committee%20at%20Ahmedgarh%2C%20Deepak%20Sharma%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20hosting%20Roza%20Iftar%20at%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20Ahmedgarh%2C%20next%20week%20for%20which%20we%20have%20sent%20invitations%20to%20all%20our%20Muslim%20friends.%20Our%20committee%20members%20will%20also%20join%20Muslim%20brothers%20for%20Eid-ul-Fitr%20celebrations.%20Earlier%20we%20used%20to%20give%20dry%20ration%20to%20financially%20weaker%20Muslim%20families%20for%20iftar%20but%20now%20we%20are%20organising%20special%20iftar%20programmes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100827%2F254d5489-4e7b-4ba6-be42-543519c01c57-768x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100827%2F254d5489-4e7b-4ba6-be42-543519c01c57-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100827%2F254d5489-4e7b-4ba6-be42-543519c01c57-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100827%2F254d5489-4e7b-4ba6-be42-543519c01c57.jpg%20864w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMuslims%20offering%20Namaz%20and%20taking%20Iftar%20at%20Gurdwara%20Singh%20Sabha%2C%20Malerkotla.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Muslims%20have%20been%20taking%20part%20in%20Hindu%20festivals%20and%20celebrations%20like%20Kanjak%20Pujan%20and%20special%20prayers%20at%20Shri%20Naina%20Devi%20Temple.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20we%20stay%20away%3F%20In%20fact%20one%20of%20our%20temple%20priests%20Raju%20Sharma%20Pandit%20even%20organised%20iftar%20at%20his%20house%20last%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%20noted%20that%20there%20are%20some%20who%20speak%20against%20Hindu-Muslim%20unity%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20we%20are%20not%20bothered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHindu-Muslim%20politics%20might%20work%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Punjab%20is%20different%20from%20UP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMalerkotla%E2%80%99s%20ties%20with%20Sri%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalerkotla%E2%80%99s%20rich%20past%20dates%20back%20to%201704%2C%20when%20the%20tenth%20Sikh%20Guru%2C%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20had%20waged%20a%20religious%20war%20against%20the%20forced%20conversion%20of%20non-Muslims%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20Mughal%20ruler%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWazir%20Khan%2C%20the%20Nawab%20of%20Sirhind%20had%20captured%20the%20two%20younger%20sons%20of%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%2C%20nine-year-old%20Zorawar%20Singh%20and%20seven-year-old%20Fateh%20Singh%20and%20ordered%20their%20executions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20Nawab%20of%20Malerkotla%2C%20Shah%20Mohammad%20Khan%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20supporter%20of%20Aurangzeb%20fought%20with%20Wazir%20Khan%20citing%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20children%20was%20against%20the%20tenets%20of%20Quran.%20The%20two%20children%20were%2C%20however%2C%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20the%20Sikhs%20built%20Gurdwara%20Haa%20Da%20Naara%20in%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99%20to%20honour%20the%20%E2%80%98rallying%20cry%20for%20justice%E2%80%99%20raised%20by%20Nawab%20Sher%20Mohammad%20Khan.%20It%20is%20one%20the%20most%20revered%20and%20iconic%20places%20of%20worship%20not%20only%20for%20the%20Sikhs%20but%20Muslims%2C%20Hindus%2C%20and%20other%20communities%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20believe%20that%20Malerkotla%20is%20blessed%20by%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20and%20Sher%20Mohammad%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20and%20that%20is%20why%20it%20has%20been%20untouched%20by%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8-1024x576.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8-1024x576.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703106%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENaseer%20Khan%20of%20Sikh%20Muslim%20Sanjhan%20Foundation%2C%20Malerkotla%20receiving%20Iftar%20gifts%20from%20a%20Sikh%20community%20member.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Adnan%20Ali%20Khan%20from%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99s%20royal%20family%20said%20that%20they%20were%20continuing%20the%20legacy%20of%20Nawab%20Sher%20Mohammad%20Khan.%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20is%20Gurdwara%20Haa%20Da%20Naara%2C%20where%20Gurbani%20Kirtan%20and%20Namaz%20are%20performed%20simultaneously%20during%20Ramzan%20or%20inviting%20Muslims%20for%20iftar%2C%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99s%20history%20is%20unique.%20Even%20during%20the%20Partition%20of%201947%2C%20Malerkotla%20remained%20untouched%20by%20religious%20hatred.%20We%20feel%20proud%20that%20the%20youngsters%20are%20also%20following%20suit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20a%20prominent%20community%20leader%20Naseer%20Khan%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20communal%20harmony%20group%2C%20Sikh-Muslim%20Sanjhan%20Foundation%20in%20Malerkotla%20said%20that%20inclusive%20iftar%20invitations%20are%20not%20just%20confined%20to%20the%20urban%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20villages%2C%20iftar%20invitations%20were%20generally%20from%20the%20Sikh%20families%20including%20the%20gurdwara%20managements.%20Just%20recently%2C%20we%20went%20for%20iftar%20to%20Gurdwara%20Singh%20Sabha%2C%20Jainpur%2C%20where%20people%20from%20seven%20villages%20like%20Lohar%20Majra%2C%20Kheri%20Jattan%2C%20Amargarh%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20were%20also%20present.%20Earlier%20we%20went%20to%20Kalain%20in%20Malerkotla%20and%20Kuthala%20villages%20in%20Sangrur%20district%20too.%20The%20list%20is%20long%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20that%20sometimes%20he%20and%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20get%20so%20many%20invitations%20from%20in%20and%20around%20Malerkotla%20that%20they%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20attend%20all%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseer%20proudly%20said%20that%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%20have%20even%20performed%20Namaz%20with%20them%2C%20a%20spectacle%20hard%20to%20find%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CMalerkotla%20has%20set%20a%20precedent%20in%20communal%20harmony%20in%20the%20country%20and%20we%20feel%20blessed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseer%20lamented%20that%20such%20stories%20were%20not%20being%20covered%20by%20the%20media%20and%20that%20was%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20from%20Malerkotla%20have%20joined%20the%20ongoing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20at%20Shambu%20border%20as%20they%20did%20the%20farmers%E2%