ctors%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20and%20Arun%20Govil%20from%20the%20Mandi%20seat%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Meerut%20seat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20respectively.%20Both%20are%20first-time%20contestants%20and%20have%20been%20vocal%20in%20their%20support%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20(in)famous%20name%20on%20the%20list%20is%20former%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20who%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20recently%20to%20join%20politics%20after%20delivering%20a%20slew%20of%20judgments%20criticising%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fi-approached-bjp-why-ex-calcutta-hc-judge-abhijit-gangopadhyays-political-plunge-sparks-questions%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20several%20experts%20believed%20his%20decision%20went%20against%20judicial%20propriety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20of%20the%20candidates%20in%20the%20listed%20constituencies%20are%20repeat%20candidates%20from%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20exceptions.%20Varun%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Pilibhit%20but%20has%20made%20a%20number%20of%20remarks%20criticising%20party%20policy%2C%20especially%20regarding%20farmers%2C%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20has%20been%20dropped%20by%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20his%20mother%20Maneka%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20given%20the%20ticket%20from%20Sultanpur%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20prominent%20names%20left%20out%20of%20candidacy%20this%20time%20are%20Union%20minister%20Ashwini%20Choubey%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20posterboy%20in%20Karnataka%20Anantkumar%20Hegde.%20Hegde%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-says-partys-400-seat-goal-for-2024-is-so-it-can-change-constitution%5C%22%3Ecreated%20a%20controversy%20recently%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20claiming%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20party%20wanted%20more%20than%20400%20seats%20this%20time%20so%20that%20it%20could%20change%20the%20Constitution.%20Choubey%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Buxar%20in%20Bihar%2C%20but%20Mithlesh%20Tiwari%20has%20been%20given%20that%20ticket%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20a%20Union%20minister%20who%20is%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20face%20from%20Odisha%2C%20has%20been%20shifted%20to%20the%20prestigious%20Sambalpur%20seat%20from%20his%20home%20seat%20Dhenkanal%2C%20which%20he%20had%20lost%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%20announced%20candidates%20for%20the%20party%20is%20a%20woman%20from%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Rekha%20Patra%2C%20from%20the%20Basirhat%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20Patra%20is%20one%20of%20the%20women%20who%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20alleged%20gender%20violence%20from%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20defectors%20have%20also%20made%20their%20way%20to%20the%20list.%20Jagadish%20Shettar%2C%20who%20recently%20switched%20back%20to%20BJP%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Belgaum%20instead%20of%20his%20home%20turf%20Hubbali-Dharwad.%20Also%2C%20former%20Congress%20MP%20and%20industrialist%20Naveen%20Jindal%2C%20whose%20company%20donated%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20had%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20has%20been%20given%20the%20ticket%20from%20Kurukshetra%2C%20his%20former%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJindal%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20electoral%20bonds%20buyer%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20list%20%E2%80%93%20Pallavi%20Dempo%20from%20the%20Dempo%20family%2C%20a%20prominent%20business%20house%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20electoral%20bond%20donor%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20Goa%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20the%20South%20Goa%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711346137000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25112422%2FBJP-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F2024-polls-bjp