my%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25104158%2FGD42QerbQAAColC.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%2C%20a%20professional%20Army%20under%20civilian%20control%2C%20has%20remained%20apolitical%20over%20the%20decades.%20However%2C%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findia-armed-forces-politicisation-by-default-or-design%5C%22%3Einstances%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20its%20apolitical%20character%20has%20been%20shaken.%20That%20this%20can%20affect%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20morale%20and%20cohesion%2C%20with%20resultant%20deleterious%20effects%20on%20national%20security%2C%20is%20a%20concern%20voiced%20by%20veterans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20connection%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-backlash-army-scraps-its-ucc-seminar-in-kashmir%5C%22%3Eone-day%20seminar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Navigating%20Legal%20Frontiers%3A%20Understanding%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%202023%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Quest%20for%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20planned%20by%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20HQ%2031%20Sub%20Area.%20It%20was%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20auditorium%2C%20and%20scheduled%20for%20March%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20see%20how%20a%20discussion%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%202023%20%E2%80%93%20replaced%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20%E2%80%93%20is%20relevant%20to%20the%20role%20or%20functioning%20of%20the%20Army.%20As%20for%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20given%20that%20it%20has%20been%20a%20politically%20highly%20loaded%20issue%20for%20years%2C%20it%20would%20best%20have%20been%20avoided%20altogether.%20Indeed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-backlash-army-scraps-its-ucc-seminar-in-kashmir%5C%22%3ELieutenant%20General%20D.S.%20Hooda%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CMy%20personal%20view%20is%20that%20any%20subject%20that%20has%20even%20the%20faintest%20whiff%20of%20politics%20or%20religion%20to%20it%20should%20be%20studiously%20avoided%20by%20the%20military%2C%20%3Cem%3Eparticularly%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20public%20discussion%20(emphasis%20added).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20is%20it%20possible%20that%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20command%20chain%20going%20up%20to%20the%20apex%2C%20was%20unaware%20of%20this%20forthcoming%20seminar%20event%20and%20its%20topics%3F%20Knowing%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Army%2C%20it%20is%20strange%20that%20the%20planning%20of%20this%20seminar%20escaped%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20commanders%20and%20their%20staff%20officers%2C%20at%20various%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seminar%20event%20being%20planned%20and%20scheduled%20for%20March%2026%20was%20due%20either%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20communication%20along%20the%20command%20chain%2C%20or%20worse%2C%20acquiescence%2Fapproval%2C%20even%20directions%20from%20higher%20headquarters.%20If%20the%20latter%2C%20it%20is%20questionable%20whether%20it%20is%20in%20consonance%20with%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20professed%20and%20widely%20appreciated%20apolitical%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlanning%20for%20this%20%E2%80%9Clegal%20awareness%20seminar%E2%80%9D%20including%20obtaining%20acceptance%20of%20the%20chief%20guest%20and%20speakers%2C%20venue%2C%20coordination%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20scheduling%20it%20for%20March%2026%2C%20would%20have%20started%20several%20weeks%20ago.%20However%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20announced%20the%20election%20schedule%20on%20March%2016.%20Notwithstanding%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-backlash-army-scraps-its-ucc-seminar-in-kashmir%5C%22%3Ethe%20invitation%20for%20the%20seminar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20reportedly%20issued%20on%20Friday%20March%2022%2C%20after%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC)%20came%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20GOC%2031%20Sub%20Area%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20specifics%20of%20the%20MCC.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20more%20than%20strange%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20who%20was%20invited%20as%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20seminar%2C%20did%20not%20advise%20the%20organisers%20that%20conducting%20the%20seminar%20on%20March%2026%20would%20violate%20the%20MCC.%20He%20could%20have%20advised%20them%20to%20cancel%20or%20postpone%20the%20event.%20Likewise%2C%20Achal%20Sethi%2C%20law%20secretary%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20a%20panelist%20at%20the%20seminar%2C%20could%20have%20advised%20HQ%2031%20Sub%20Area%20similarly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seminar%20being%20planned%20by%20our%20nation%E2%80%99s%20last%20bastion%20against%20the%20prevalent%20communal%20divisiveness%2C%20and%20then%20cancelled%20only%20after%20a%20public%20outcry%2C%20does%20not%20speak%20well%20for%20the%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20various%20acts%20of%20commission%20and%20omission%20by%20the%20military%20and%20civil%20administrations%20relating%20to%20the%20seminar%20are%20cause%20for%20deep%20disappointment%20for%20this%20writer%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20an%20apolitical%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMajor%20General%20S.G.%20Vombatkere%20retired%20in%201996%2C%20as%20Additional%20Director%20General%20(Discipline%20and%20Vigilance)%2C%20in%20the%20Army%20Headquarters%20Adjutant%20General%E2%80%99s%20Branch.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711343562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25104158%2FGD42QerbQAAColC.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fa-veterans-concerns-about-an-increasingly-political-army%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20seminar%20on%20the%20UCC%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%93%20planned%20and%20then%20cancelled%20%E2%80%93%20does%20not%20speak%20well%20for%20the%20