%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68650914.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Moves%20SC%20Against%20President%20Murmu%20for%20Withholding%20Assent%20to%20State%20Bills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20March%2023%2C%20Kerala%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu%20for%20withholding%20assent%20to%20four%20out%20of%20seven%20bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala-moves-supreme-court-against-president-withholding-assent-four-bills%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKerala%20has%20also%20moved%20the%20court%20against%20Governor%20Mohammed%20Arif%20Khan%20for%20keeping%20his%20assent%20on%20bills%20pending%20for%20months%20%E2%80%93%20from%20between%20seven%20to%2024%20months%20%E2%80%94%20and%20referring%20them%20to%20Murmu%20when%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFour%20of%20seven%20bills%20not%20given%20assent%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Kerala%20state%20assembly%20passed%20several%20bills%20including%20seven%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20were%20also%20in%20public%20interest%20%E2%80%94%20the%20state%20said%20as%20it%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20Murmu%20for%20withholding%20assent%20to%20four%20of%20those%20seven%20bills.%20The%20president%20has%20also%20not%20given%20any%20reason%20for%20withholding%20assent%20to%20these%20bills%2C%20Kerala%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20president%20withholding%20assent%20to%20the%20bills%20%E2%80%9Csubverts%20and%20disrupts%E2%80%9D%20the%20federal%20structure%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seven%20bills%20included%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20amendments%20to%20the%20University%20Laws%20(dated%202021%20and%202022)%2C%20the%20Kerala%20Lokayukta%20Amendment%20bill%20and%20the%20Kerala%20Cooperative%20Societies%20Amendment%20bill%20of%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20the%20seven%20bills%20pertained%20to%20Centre-state%20relations%20and%20therefore%20did%20not%20require%20the%20assent%20of%20the%20President%2C%20Kerala%20maintained%20in%20its%20argument%20at%20the%20Court%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKerala%20challenges%20actions%20of%20governor%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kerala%20government%20has%20also%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20its%20governor%20Mohammmed%20Arif%20Khan%20for%20reserving%20the%20seven%20bills%20for%20the%20President%20when%20he%20could%20have%20dealt%20with%20them%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20has%20argued%20in%20its%20petition%20that%20two%20of%20the%20seven%20bills%20remained%20with%20the%20governor%20for%20around%2024%20months%20before%20he%20passed%20it%20to%20the%20President%20for%20assent%3B%20the%20other%20five%20remained%20with%20the%20governor%20for%20between%20seven%20to%2016%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20inaction%20regarding%20the%20bills%20has%20%E2%80%9Csubverted%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20legislature%20of%20the%20state%20and%20rendered%20its%20existence%20itself%20ineffective%20and%20otiose%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBarAndBench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKerala%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20governor%20did%20not%20inform%20the%20President%20that%20the%20bills%20remained%20with%20him%20for%20so%20many%20months%2C%20pending%20assent.%20This%20amounts%20to%20a%20violation%20of%20Article%20200%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20as%20per%20which%20the%20governor%20has%20to%20send%20such%20bills%20to%20the%20President%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20Kerala%2C%20states%20such%20as%20Punjab%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Telangana%20have%20raised%20similar%20concerns%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20about%20their%20governors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711292099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkerala-moves-sc-against-president-murmu-for-withholding-assent-to-state-bills%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20has%20also%20moved%20the%20court%20against%20Governor%20Mohammed%20Arif%20Khan%20for%20keeping%20his%20assent%20on%20bills%20pending%20for%20months%20and%20then%20referring%20them%20to%20Murmu%20when%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkerala-moves-sc-against-president-murmu-for-withholding-assent-to-state-bills%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Waiters%20carrying%20croissants%20race%20through%20Paris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711292026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F53AC%2Fproduction%2F_133002412_p0hlmjf1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68649600%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20competition%20for%20waiters%20and%20waitresses%20began%20in%201914%2C%20but%20has%20not%20been%20held%20since%202011%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20sponsors.%22%