-says-all-four-gunmen-arrested-after-133-killed-in-moscow-concert-hall-attack-13100843%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fputin-says-all-four-gunmen-arrested-after-133-killed-in-moscow-concert-hall-attack-13100843%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Go%20For%20Coaching%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20Ex-IRS%20Officer%E2%80%99s%20Free%20UPSC%20CSE%20Course%20Eliminates%20Need%20for%20Paid%20Classes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20millions%20of%20Indians%20want%20to%20get%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342929%2Fias-sonal-goel-upsc-cse-mains-preparation-strategy-for-general-studies-topper-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnion%20civil%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20very%20few%20decide%20to%20quit%20it%20once%20they%20achieve%20their%20dream.%20So%2C%20why%20did%20Ravi%20Kapoor%2C%20a%20former%20officer%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263491%2Firs-officer-cse-upsc-exam-how-to-pass-cracking-fail-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Revenue%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%20(IRS)%20of%20the%202011%20batch%2C%20decide%20to%20formally%20quit%20a%20year%20ago%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20interested%20in%20the%20subject%20matter%2C%20i.e.%20taxation.%20Guided%20by%20service%20rules%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20accounting%20and%20number-based%20type%20of%20work%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20involve%20too%20much%20creativity.%20Working%20in%20the%20IRS%20also%20vests%20you%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20power.%20I%20was%20neither%20interested%20in%20the%20subject%20matter%20nor%20the%20pursuit%20of%20power.%20The%20work%20was%20suffocating%20my%20curiosity%20and%20my%20energy.%20My%20heart%20was%20just%20not%20in%20it.%20That%20is%20the%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20service%2C%20however%2C%20Ravi%20found%20an%20avenue%20that%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20quit%E2%80%94mentoring%20UPSC%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%20aspirants.%20Since%202020%2C%20Ravi%20has%20been%20running%20a%20Free%20Online%20Mentorship%20Programme%20(FMP)%20for%20thousands%20of%20aspirants%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20the%20Chief%20Mentor%20of%20UPSC%20at%20Testbook%2C%20an%20online%20exam%20preparation%20platform.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20upon%20his%2010%20years%20of%20bureaucratic%20experience%20and%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20clinical%20psychology%2C%20Ravi%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20UPSC%20mentorship%20has%20always%20been%20geared%20towards%20mental%20fitness%20and%20motivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20results%20of%20his%20FMP%20have%20been%20promising.%20Last%20year%2C%207%20of%20his%20students%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20exam.%20This%20year%20they%E2%80%99re%20expecting%20around%2020%20students%20to%20clear%20the%20exam.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20FMP%20has%20given%20UPSC%20aspirants%20a%20choice%2C%20which%20is%20what%20stands%20out%20the%20most%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Free%20UPSC%20CSE%20Coaching%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095.jpg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_385505274338974_41262283478126641_n_1080-1710948095-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_433239338_3855052743