these%20institutes%20to%20guide%20them%20through%20a%20process%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20guide%20and%20plan%20%5Bthe%20course%5D%20themselves.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ravi%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20students%20are%20given%20the%20choice%20of%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20attend%20coaching%20institutes%20or%20not.%20That%20choice%20did%20not%20really%20exist%20earlier.%20Much%20of%20the%20mentorship%20and%20guidance%20is%20in%20courses%20like%20our%20FMP%C2%A0%20just%20like%20the%20content%20is%20also%20available%20everywhere.%20If%20you%20use%20them%20both%20smartly%2C%20you%20can%20bypass%20the%20requirement%20of%20coaching.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20choice%20has%20to%20be%20with%20the%20consumer%20(aspirant).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20quit%20a%20desirable%20occupation%20to%20mentor%20UPSC%20aspirants%20and%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%20established%20by%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20comes%20from%20facing%20the%20drawbacks%20of%20the%20conventional%20school%20education%20system%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FRavi-Sir-Image-1710948207.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Kapoor%20runs%20a%20free%20course%20for%20UPSC%20aspirants%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FRavi-Sir-Image-1710948207.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FRavi-Sir-Image-1710948207-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FRavi-Sir-Image-1710948207-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FRavi-Sir-Image-1710948207-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FRavi-Sir-Image-1710948207-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345404%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERavi%20Kapoor%20runs%20a%20Free%20Mentorship%20Programme%20(FMP)%20for%20UPSC%20aspirants.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20education%20system%20failed%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20modest%20middle-class%20family%20in%20West%20Delhi%2C%20Ravi%20grew%20up%20with%20his%20share%20of%20struggles.%20During%20his%20teens%2C%20Ravi%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292695%2Fhealthy-weight-loss-diet-daily-workout-helped-me-lose-110-kg%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverweight%20boy%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20no%20noteworthy%20academic%20achievements.%20He%20suffered%20bullying%20and%20isolation%2C%20which%20led%20to%20growing%20introversion%20and%20was%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20his%20self-esteem.%20Only%20later%20did%20he%20understand%20that%20he%20had%20Attention%20Deficit%20Disorder%20(ADD)%2C%20the%20diagnosis%20of%20which%20helped%20him%20identify%20and%20help%20himself%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisappointed%20with%20the%20traditional%20education%20system%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20tailored%20to%20neurodivergent%20students%20like%20him%2C%20and%20to%20overcome%20his%20feelings%20of%20inferiority%2C%20Ravi%20shifted%20his%20focus%20to%20physical%20fitness%20and%20bodybuilding.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20rebellious%20teenager%2C%20I%20felt%20school%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20drop%20education%20altogether.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20career%20in%20sports.%20Despite%20trying%20to%20make%20something%20of%20these%20pursuits%20even%20after%20college%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20because%20people%20like%20me%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20necessary%20support%20structure%20or%20infrastructure%20to%20excel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20theme%20in%20Ravi%E2%80%99s%20early%20life%20is%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20school%20education%20system%20in%20India%20to%20help%20students%20like%20him%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20pursue%20conventional%20careers%20in%20engineering%20and%20medicine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20got%20to%20explore%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20just%20because%20my%20academic%20inclinations%20were%20unconventional.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Class%2010%2C%20I%20was%20fascinated%20by%20philosophy%20and%20psychology.%20Although%20I%20wanted%20to%20opt%20for%20them%20in%20high%20school%2C%20neither%20my%20parents%2C%20teachers%20nor%20mentors%20allowed%20me%20to.%20Not%20only%20was%20I%20denied%20the%20chance%20to%20study%20these%20subjects%20but%20I%20was%20also%20judged%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20around%20me%20told%20me%20that%20%E2%80%98serious%20and%20successful%20people%E2%80%99%20don%E2%80%99t%20engage%20with%20these%20subjects.%20A%20major%20failure%20of%20the%20school%20education%20system%20is%20its%20inability%20to%20encourage%20obvious%20interest%20in%20areas%20deemed%20%E2%80%98unconventional%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20after%20Class%2012%2C%20Ravi%20applied%20for%20a%20Psychology%20(Honours)%20course%20at%20Zakir%20Hussain%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University%2C%20and%20was%20even%20accepted.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20path%20he%20wanted%20to%20take.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20was%20pushed%20towards%20engineering.%20Ironically%2C%20I%20cleared%20my%20UPSC%20civil%20services%20exam%20choosing%20psychology%20as%20one%20of%20my%20optional%20subjects%20and%20recently%20earned%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20it.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20take%20such%20a%20long-winded%20road%20to%20pursue%20my%20real%20academic%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20muses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20he%20argues%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340832%2Fadvanced-stem-learning-helps-6000-students-in-govt-schools-innovate-thanks-to-one-initiative%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20education%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20large%20extent%20overlooks%20children%20who%20aren%E2%80%99t%20neurotypical.%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20was%20quite%20severely%20attention%20deficient%20and%20this%20was%20quite%20obvious.%20But%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20given%20the%20kind%20of%20care%20and%20attention%20any%20such%20child%20needs.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20everyone%20pushes%20you%20towards%20science.%20Although%20I%20did%20eventually%20develop%20an%20interest%20in%20engineering%20much%20later%20in%20life%2C%20there%20was%20this%20external%20push%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20clarity%20in%20UPSC%20preparations%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20perception%20of%20preparing%20for%20the%20gruelling%20three-part%20UPSC%20civil%20services%20exam%20is%20that%20it%20requires%20rote%20learning%20and%20parsing%20through%20vast%20amounts%20of%20reading%20material.%20For%20Ravi%2C%20however%2C%20UPSC%20preparations%20filled%20those%20significant%20knowledge%20gaps%20created%20in%20school%20and%20college.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20aspirant%2C%20I%20learnt%20everything%20from%20scratch.%20I%20filled%20all%20those%20gaps%20in%20my%20education%2C%20learning%20and%20understanding%20about%20the%20world%2C%20and%20how%20things%20actually%20connect%20and%20attained%20a%20degree%20of%20conceptual%20clarity%20during%20my%20UPSC%20preparations.%20I%20never%20achieved%20this%20level%20of%20clarity%20in%20school.%20This%20revelation%2C%20following%20my%20preparation%2C%20made%20me%20a%20different%20person%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20vividly%20remembers%20a%20few%20moments%20that%20led%20to%20this%20intellectual%20awakening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20went%20to%20coaching%20institutes%20and%20understood%20nothing.%20My%20preferred%20subject%2C%20and%20one%20of%20my%20optional%20subjects%20(for%20the%20Mains%20exam)%20was%20Psychology%2C%20given%20my%20proficiency%20in%20it%20despite%20having%20no%20academic%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20reading%20a%20chapter%20on%20motivation%2C%20I%20discovered%20theories%20about%20what%20motivates%20people.%20There%20were%20parts%20about%20how%20childhood%20influences%20make%20a%20person%20the%20way%20they%20are%2C%20how%20one%20can%20bring%20out%20their%20true%20potential%20and%20the%20roadblocks%20along%20the%20way.%20Reading%20such%20material%20gave%20me%20answers%20to%20the%20questions%20that%20I%20always%20had.%20To%20me%2C%20this%20was%20real%20knowledge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20I%20taught%20these%20things%20instead%20of%20Physics%3F%20This%20is%20the%20stuff%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20because%20these%20concepts%20helped%20me%20explain%20my%20behaviour%20and%20the%20behaviour%20of%20people%20around%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20concepts%20gave%20him%20a%20degree%20of%20emotional%20and%20intellectual%20maturity%20that%20was%20missing%20in%20his%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20then%2C%20everything%20I%20saw%20and%20learned%20was%20connected%20to%20how%20it%20pertains%20to%20real%20life.%20I%20began%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20world%20as%20it%20is%20rather%20than%20what%20I%20read%20in%20books.%20For%20example%2C%20UPSC%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20ask%20you%20questions%20like%20who%20made%20UPI%20or%20to%20give%20its%20full%20form.%20They%20will%20rather%20ask%20you%2C%20when%20you%20root%20a%20transaction%20through%20UPI%2C%20what%20are%20the%20banking%20channels%20it%20goes%20through%20and%20why%2C%20what%20are%20the%20problems%20with%20UPI%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20vantage%20point%20of%20UPSC%20is%20not%20that%20of%20a%20supervisor%20sitting%20in%20an%20ivory%20tower%20and%20judging%20people%20below.%20When%20you%20see%20the%20world%20as%20a%20UPSC%20aspirant%2C%20you%20interconnect%20things%2C%20find%20solutions%20and%20ask%20various%20questions.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20skip%20a%20red%20light%20and%20a%20traffic%20policeman%20gives%20me%20a%20fine.%20Under%20what%20law%20is%20the%20traffic%20policeman%20given%20the%20authority%20to%20slap%20a%20fine%20on%20me%3F%20What%20happens%20if%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20pay%20the%20fine%3F%20Where%20does%20the%20authority%20to%20punish%20me%20for%20not%20paying%20the%20fine%20come%20from%3F%20You%20ask%20these%20questions%20and%20begin%20to%20realise%20how%20this%20system%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_320588210_697350065423806_3553989600011319296_n_1080-1710948453.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Free%20course%20for%20UPSC%20aspirants%20by%20Ravi%20Kapoor%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_320588210_697350065423806_3553989600011319296_n_1080-1710948453.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_320588210_697350065423806_3553989600011319296_n_1080-1710948453-300x265.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSnapinsta.app_320588210_697350065423806_3553