20the%20same%20village%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20remembered%20how%20some%20kids%20had%20gone%20out%20to%20graze%20their%20cows%20and%20goats.%20Everyone%20was%20restless.%20After%20some%20time%2C%20we%20saw%20them%20returning%20from%20the%20burning%20forest.%20While%20they%20had%20sustained%20severe%20burns%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20their%20goats%20had%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20happens%20almost%20every%20year%20in%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252324%2Fjharkhand-ifs-hero-solution-forest-fires-dry-leaves-briquettes-ecofriendly-innovation-earns-village-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20fire%20season%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%202022%2C%20a%20total%20of%201%2C443%20incidents%20of%20forest%20fires%20were%20reported%20%E2%80%94%20including%20642%20in%20Garhwal%2C%20724%20in%20Kumaon%2C%20and%2077%20in%20protected%20wildlife%20zones.%20This%20was%20estimated%20to%20affect%202%2C432.62%20hectares%20of%20forest%20area%20and%20an%20economic%20loss%20of%20over%20Rs%2060%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pritam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20young%20volunteers%2C%20are%20leading%20the%20charge%20against%20forest%20fires%20to%20protect%20their%20land.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711-