st%20cover%20in%20Uttarakhand%20is%2024%2C303.04%20sq%20km%2C%20which%20is%2045.44%20percent%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20geographical%20area.%20And%20of%20the%20total%20forest%20cover%2C%20more%20than%20one-third%20(32.75%20percent)%20is%20prone%20to%20forest%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fforest-fire-1-1711027591.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pritam%20requests%20local%20people%20in%20the%20fire-prone%20regions%20to%20step%20up%20and%20respond%20to%20emergencies.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fforest-fire-1-1711027591.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fforest-fire-1-1711027591-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fforest-fire-1-1711027591-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fforest-fire-1-1711027591-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fforest-fire-1-1711027591-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPritam%20requests%20local%20people%20in%20the%20fire-prone%20regions%20to%20step%20up%20and%20respond%20to%20emergencies.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20reasons%20that%20cause%20forest%20fires%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIncidences%20of%20forest%20fires%20are%20common%20between%20February%20and%20mid-July.%20These%20fires%20are%20exacerbated%20largely%20by%20human%20activities%20such%20as%20slash-and-burn%20agriculture%2C%20the%20use%20of%20fire%20for%20land%20clearance%2C%20and%20reckless%20disposal%20of%20lit%20%3Cem%3Ebeedi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20cigarettes.%20Besides%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20myth%20among%20local%20villagers%20that%20if%20they%20set%20the%20forest%20ablaze%2C%20it%20induces%20rain%20that%20will%20yield%20nutritious%20fodder%20for%20livestock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20fires%20not%20only%20result%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20valuable%20forest%20resources%20and%20wildlife%20but%20also%20affect%20humans%20in%20direct%20and%20indirect%20ways.%20It%20pollutes%20our%20water%20sources%20that%20originate%20from%20forests.%20It%20also%20increases%20their%20risk%20of%20drying%20up.%20Usually%2C%20villagers%20store%20firewood%20and%20fodder%20in%20their%20homes.%20And%20when%20these%20forest%20fires%20reach%20these%20habitations%2C%20they%20take%20a%20dreadful%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20Uttarakhand%20accounts%20for%201.6%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20geographical%20area.%20But%20in%20terms%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250621%2Fforest-fires-save-pradeep-mirase-ifs-similipal-malkangiri-environment-biodiversity-hero-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20cover%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20state%20accounts%20for%2045%20percent%20compared%20to%20national%20forest%20cover%20of%20just%2021.67%20percent%20%E2%80%94%20this%20signifies%20the%20rich%20biological%20heritage%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20urgency%20to%20save%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20carbon%20sinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20the%20need%20to%20preserve%20the%20rich%20flora%20and%20fauna%20of%20the%20state%2C%20in%202022%2C%20the%20Delhi-NCR-based%20NGO%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20began%20community-driven%20efforts%20to%20decrease%20forest%20fires%20in%20the%20state%20and%20promote%20environmental%20conservation%20and%20ecological%20balance.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20initiative%2C%20the%20foundation%20enlisted%20volunteer%20firefighters%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Pritam%20%E2%80%94%20to%20reduce%20forest%20fire%20occurrences.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Of%20the%20total%20forest%20cover%20of%20the%20state%2C%20more%20than%20one-third%20is%20prone%20to%20forest%20fires.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1-1711021742-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345442%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOf%20the%20total%20forest%20cover%20of%20the%20state%2C%20more%20than%20one-third%20is%20prone%20to%20forest%20fires.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreventing%20fires%20through%20community%20participation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20Pritam%2C%20like%20many%20other%20volunteers%2C%20was%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20was%20better%20equipped%20and%20prepared%20for%20any%20untoward%20incidents%20similar%20to%20those%20that%20occurred%20in%202022%20and%20was%20able%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20emergency%20and%20control%20potential%20fire%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20educated%20on%20how%20to%20implement%20local%20mitigation%20strategies%20to%20effectively%20control%20any%20forest%20fire.%20We%20were%20provided%20with%20firefighting%20kits%20that%20included%20a%20set%20of%20different%20types%20of%20fire%20rakes%2C%20a%20modified%20sickle%2C%20a%20shovel%2C%20a%20fire%20beater%2C%20and%20a%20tool%20kit%20bag.%20Training%20was%20provided%20on%20fire%20line%20development%2C%20biomass%20management%2C%20safety%20measures%20during%20fire%20dousing%2C%20and%20uses%20of%20the%20various%20equipment%20that%20were%20provided%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20he%20responds%20to%20the%20emergency%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20inform%20the%20forest%20department%20about%20any%20forest%20fires%20that%20occur%20in%20the%20area.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20start%20clearing%20broad%20strips%20of%20land%20of%20all%20inflammable%20material%20like%20dry%20leaves%20and%20fodder%20so%20that%20fire%20does%20not%20extend%20from%20one%20area%20to%20another.%20After%20making%20forest%20lines%2C%20we%20also%20throw%20sand%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20fire%20is%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20we%20try%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20spreading%20further%20rather%20than%20extinguishing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Following%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20many%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345443%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFollowing%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20many%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Pritam%2C%20THF%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20of%20preventing%20forest%20fire%20has%20seen%205%2C066%20young%20firefighters%20being%20trained%20in%201%2C000%20villages%20under%2010%20development%20blocks%20of%20Pauri%20Garhwal%2C%20Tehri%20Garhwal%2C%20Almora%2C%20and%20Bageshwar%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20THF%20has%20also%20enhanced%20community%20resilience%20by%20reviving%20the%20%E2%80%98Van%20Panchayat%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20local%20community%20group%20responsible%20for%20forest%20management%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encouraging%20the%20plantation%20of%20fire-resistant%20species%2C%20and%20raising%20awareness%20through%20%3Cem%3ENukkad%20Natak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(street%20play)%2C%20rallies%2C%20wall%20writing%2C%20quiz%20competition%2C%20radio%20programs%2C%20and%20jingles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20region%20has%20observed%20a%20significant%20decrease%20of%20about%2053.33%20percent%20%E2%80%94%20from%2030%20forest%20fire%20incidents%20in%202019-21%20to%2014%20in%202022.%20Similarly%2C%20a%2057.35%20percent%20reduction%20was%20observed%20in%20the%20area%20affected%20by%20forest%20fires%20%E2%80%94%20from%2037.05%20to%2015.8%20hectares%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraged%20by%20the%20results%20of%20the%20community-driven%20approach%2C%20Pritam%20requests%20local%20people%20in%20the%20fire-prone%20regions%20to%20step%20up%20and%20respond%20to%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ejal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(water)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejungle%20%3C%2Fem%3E(forest)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejameen%20%3C%2Fem%3E(land)%20belong%20to%20all%20of%20us%20as%20a%20community%2C%20so%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20step%20up%20to%20safeguard%20it.%20We%20need%20to%20take%20more%20responsibility%20and%20consciously%20increase%20our%20awareness%20against%20forest%20fires.%20In%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20bust%20myths%20among%20villagers%20and%20reduce%20extreme%20forest%20fire%20incidences%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pritam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20could%20do%20it%2C%20then%20you%20too%20can.%20This%20Forest%20Day%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20pledge%20to%20save%20our%20jungles!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fukhand-loses-highest-561-2-ha-green-cover-in-24hrs-to-fires-over-2k-ha-so-far%2Farticleshow%2F91136591.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUttarakhand%20loses%20highest%20561.2%20ha%20green%20cover%20in%2024%20hours%20to%20fires%3B%20over%202%2C000%20ha%20so%20far%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3A%20by%20Shivani%20Azad%20for%20The%20Times%20of%20India%2C%20Published%20on%2028%20April%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffsi.nic.in%2Fisfr19%2Fvol2%2Fisfr-2019-vol-ii-uttarakhand.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20State%20of%20Forest%20Report%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Forest%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20Published%20in%202019.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711026101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-1711021711.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Community-driven%20efforts%20led%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20in%20Uttarakhand%20have%20effectively%20reduced%20forest%20fire%20incidents%20in%201%2C000%20villages%20amidst%20rising%20cases%20due%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20human%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345435%2Fyouth-fight-forest-fires-in-uttarakhand-the-hans-foundation-initiative-save-jungles%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%207%20Women-Led%20Startups%20of%20India%20Are%20Driving%20Impact%20at%20Scale%20in%20Climate%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20Villgro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20culinary%2C%20cosmetics%2C%20green%20energy%2C%20or%20agriculture%2C%20women%20have%20created%20a%20niche%20in%20every%20sector%20of%20the%20Indian%20market.%20According%20to%20a%20WISER%20%E2%80%94%20Women%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Startup%20Ecosystem%20Report%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345065%2Fhow-to-find-a-lawyer-legal-startup-pune-shreya-sharma-divorce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen-led%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20risen%20to%2018%20percent%20in%20the%20country%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20But%20while%20this%20is%20a%20poster%20story%20of%20the%20success%20that%20the%20female%20entrepreneurial%20world%20has%20witnessed%2C%20another%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EDealStreetAsia%3C%2Fem%3E%20claims%20that%20startups%20founded%20by%20women%20received%20only%200.3%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20venture%20capital%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20growth%20is%20a%20series%20of%20small%20steps%2C%20Cisco%20and%20Villgro%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20enterprise%20incubator%20%E2%80%94%20have%20come%20up%20with%20a%20joint%20initiative%2C%20%E2%80%98Tvaran%E2%80%99%2C%20whose%20intent%20is%20to%20introduce%20progressive%20changes%20to%20the%20way%20women-led%20startups%20are%20being%20empowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20first%20cohort%2C%20launched%20in%20October%202022%2C%20met%20its%20goal%20of%20accelerating%20women%20entrepreneurs%20driving%20innovative%20solutions%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20sector%20by%20providing%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20specifically%20climate%20action%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kalyani%20Krishna%2C%20Manager%2C%20Gender%20Inclusion%20Villgro%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman-induced%20climate%20change%20is%20not%20just%20hearsay%2C%20she%20cautions.%20A%202020%20research%20initiative%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20Climate%20Change%20Research%20(CCCR)%20in%20India%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20(MoES)%20revealed%20a%20rise%20of%200.7%20degrees%20Celsius%20surface%20air%20temperature%20from%201901%20to%202018%20and%20a%20rise%20of%201%20degree%20Celsius%20sea%20surface%20temperatures%20in%20the%20tropical%20Indian%20Ocean%20from%201951%20to%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20climate%20action%20startups%2C%20you%20ask%3F%20Why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%20She%20emphasises%20how%20Tvaran%20is%20tying%20two%20goals%20into%20one%20by%20backing%20women%20business%20owners%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20champions%20of%20climate%20advocacy.%20Early-stage%20women%20entrepreneurs%20are%20being%20supported%20by%20helping%20them%20amplify%20their%20market%20presence.%20This%20is%20being%20achieved%20by%20giving%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance%2C%20which%20will%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20help%20them%20commercialise%20and%20scale%20their%20ventures%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalyani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201805px)%20100vw%2C%201805px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221805%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sectors%20where%20women%20are%20taking%20charge%20of%20businesses%20has%20expanded%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%201805w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-1536x2048.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20sectors%20where%20women%20are%20taking%20charge%20of%20businesses%20have%20expanded%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.