apanese%20food%20and%20more%2C%20there%20was%20a%20stall%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306970%2Finspired-by-mom-entrepreneur-opens-nepali-restaurant-in-uttarakhand-mitho-thakali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20momos%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20Ankita%20and%20Impreet%20watched%20with%20bated%20breath%20as%20people%20came%20to%20see%20what%20the%20hype%20was%20all%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20gave%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20test%20the%20market.%20What%20we%20observed%20was%20that%20though%20people%20did%20not%20know%20much%20about%20the%20momos%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20try%20it%20out.%20Once%20they%20sampled%20it%2C%20they%20would%20return%20for%20some%20more.%20We%20developed%20a%20small%20fan%20base%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20that%20the%20idea%20would%20do%20well%2C%20the%20duo%20bought%20a%20food%20truck%20and%20started%20a%20business%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20add%20that%20they%20continue%20to%20serve%20momos%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20food%20festival%20in%20New%20York%20that%20runs%20from%20April%20through%20October.%20To%20cater%20to%20every%20diaspora%2C%20the%20menu%20is%20divided%20into%20subtle%20options.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20butter%20garlic%20momos%20are%20a%20hit%20with%20the%20Americans%20while%20the%20spicier%20options%20suit%20the%20Indian%20palate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20emphasise%2C%20however%2C%20that%20perfecting%20the%20momo%20recipe%20has%20been%20a%20challenge.%20Eight%20months%20of%20experimenting%20finally%20led%20them%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20momo%20that%20had%20the%20ideal%20wrapper%20size%2C%20one%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20too%20chewy%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20thick%20enough%20to%20hold%20the%20herbs%20and%20spices%20and%20veggies%2C%20and%20of%20course%20a%20momo%20that%20ticked%20all%20the%20boxes%20for%20taste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20been%20telling.%20As%20the%20clock%20strikes%205%20pm%2C%20Ankita%20and%20Impreet%20brace%20themselves%20for%20the%20office%20crowd%20that%20will%20soon%20be%20stopping%20at%20the%20food%20truck%20for%20their%20snack.%20The%20sizzles%20and%20chopping%20sounds%20travel%20through%20the%20call%20as%20they%20prepare%20the%20fillings%20for%20the%20momos%20for%20the%20hungry%20customers%20who%20will%20soon%20be%20there.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710943576000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fmomos-_11zon-1709902674.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344409%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Techies%20by%20the%20day%2C%20chefs%20by%20night%2C%20Ankita%20Nagpal%20and%20Impreet%20Sodhi%20run%20the%20Fomo%20Momo%20food%20truck%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20Here's%20how%20they%20went%20about%20setting%20up%20a%20business%20based%20on%20a%20taste%20they%20missed%20so%20much.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344409%2Ffomo-momo-food-truck-new-jersey-serves-tandoori-butter-garlic-momos-women-missed-delhi%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20%2440%20Million%20in%20Funding%2C%20Indian%20Startup%20Creates%20%E2%80%98SUV%20of%20EV%20Scooters%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20about%20the%20electronic%20two-wheeler%20market%20in%20India%20with%20the%20co-founder%20of%20River%2C%20an%20EV%20startup%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20what%20we%20both%20agreed%20upon%20was%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302187%2Fchennai-startup-electric-vehicle-two-wheelers-in-africa-electric-autos-and-e-mobility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20that%20two-wheelers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20India%20are%20the%20best%20friends%20of%20any%20middle-class%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20use%20it%20for%20everything%20from%20travelling%20in%20the%20city%20to%20buying%20groceries.%20That%20means%20that%20these%20families%20need%20their%20two-wheelers%20to%20have%20ample%20space%2C%20efficiency%20and%20be%20cost-effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aravind%20Mani%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECracking%20the%20code%2C%20Aravind%2C%20along%20with%20his%20co-founder%2C%20Vipin%20George%2C%20made%20their%20electric%20two-wheeler%20with%2055%20litre%20of%20storage%20space%2C%20packing%20it%20with%20numerous%20qualities.%20Calling%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98SUV%20of%20Scooters%E2%80%99%2C%20Indie%20is%20an%20electric%20two-wheeler%20built%20under%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20recently%20raised%20an%20investment%20of%20%2440%20million%20(Rs%20335%20crore)%20globally%20in%20an%20oversubscribed%20Series%20A%20and%20Series%20B%20round%20(second%20round%20of%20funding).%20Interestingly%2C%20Yamaha%20Motor%20Company%20and%20UAE%20automotive%20giant%2C%20Al-Futtaim%2C%20are%20among%20its%20top%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20their%20partnership%20a%20perfect%20match%2C%20Aravind%20explains%20how%20their%20work%20at%20the%20startup%20is%20divided.%20%E2%80%9CVipin%20is%20a%20hardcore%20automobile%20guy%20and%20I%20know%20how%20to%20sell%20things.%20The%20combination%20is%20perfect%20and%20we%20both%20handle%20our%20respective%20areas%20of%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20co-founders%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332097%2Fkerala-sustainable-home-disaster-resistant-ecofriendly-lgsf-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20are%20from%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%20a