ssing%20how%20the%20conclave%20helped%20them%20resolve%20social%20and%20economic%20challenges%20within%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20500%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20open-air%20Amphitheatre%20at%20Tribal%20Culture%20Centre%20(TCC)%20for%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAkhra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20journey%20through%20powerful%20personal%20and%20collective%20narratives%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESamuday%20ke%20Saath%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20platform%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344734%2Ftata-samvaad-jamshedpur-sumanti-devi-artisan-preserves-oraon-art-mud-natural-finger-painting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshare%20one%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20expressions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20own%20life%E2%80%99s%20trajectory%20or%20inspired%20by%20others%E2%80%99%20lived%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Samvaad%20has%20celebrated%20and%20brought%20together%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20individuals%20from%20over%20200%20tribes%20in%20India%20and%2017%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0960_11zon-1710505353-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Participants%20displaying%20the%20popular%20food%20items%20from%20their%20tribal%20communities%20at%20the%20stalls%20in%20Samvaad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0960_11zon-1710505353-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0960_11zon-1710505353-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0960_11zon-1710505353-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%