ell%20as%20money.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20to%20spend%20two%20days%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20which%20posed%20a%20major%20challenge%20due%20to%20travelling%2C%20especially%20considering%20I%20reside%20in%20a%20hilly%20area%20with%20rugged%20terrain.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20have%20no%20one%20to%20accompany%20me%20as%20my%20son%20attends%20college.%20Enduring%20this%20commute%20for%20almost%20four%20months%20left%20me%20exhausted%20and%20made%20work%20exceedingly%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202022%2C%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centre%20opened%20its%20doors%20in%20Karnaprayag%2C%20a%20mere%20half-hour%20journey%20from%20Chandrakala%E2%80%99s%20residence.%20This%20reduced%20her%20travel%20time%2C%20ensuring%20that%20she%20could%20return%20home%20within%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20day%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20promptly%20fulfil%20her%20duties%20as%20an%20ASHA%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20kidney%20health%3A%20dialysis%2C%20costs%2C%20and%20access%20initiatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealthy%20kidneys%20cleanse%20your%20blood%2C%20removing%20waste%20and%20excess%20fluid%20from%20your%20body%20in%20the%20form%20of%20urine.%20They%20also%20regulate%20acidity%20levels%20and%20contribute%20to%20maintaining%20a%20proper%20balance%20of%20water%2C%20salts%2C%20and%20minerals%20in%20your%20bloodstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20kidneys%20are%20unable%20to%20remove%20enough%20wastes%20and%20fluids%20from%20the%20blood%2C%20it%20causes%20a%20build-up%20of%20toxins%20and%20waste.%20Dialysis%20replaces%20the%20functions%20of%20the%20kidney%20by%20removing%20the%20waste%20and%20excess%20fluid%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Ganpat%20Ram%2C%20Medical%20Officer%20at%20Karnaprayag%20Renal%20Care%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%